(6, 'Boeung Ket FC rope in first ASEAN COTA player into squad', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Boeung Ket FC signed 24-year-old left-back Scott Woods from the Philippines on Thursday, making him the first ASEAN COTA player in the club.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Woods joined the four-time CPL winners Boeung Ket FC after fulfilling his duty with the Philippines National Football Team in the ASEAN Mitsubishi Electric Cup 2024. Woods played a key role in guiding his side to the tournament&rsquo;s semifinals. However, Thailand defeated them bringing their tournament journey to an end.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Before joining Boeung Ket FC, Woods played for Muangthong United in Thailand&rsquo;s first professional football league.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The CPL altered their regulations for foreign player registration ahead of the season 2023-2024, with each club in the league allowed to register six foreign players, one of whom must be from Asia and another from inside ASEAN.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The CPL hoped to improve league quality and support ASEAN players in doing so, which has hitherto never been done.</p>', 'Admin', '2025-01-07 06:55:31', 'uploads/677ccfe30809a.jpg', 1, 1, '2025-02-06 15:52:59', 318),
(7, 'Cambodia marks ASEAN Sports Day 2024 in Phnom Penh', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cambodia marked on Saturday the ASEAN Sports Day 2024 at the National Olympic Stadium in Phnom Penh to strengthen and promote sports in all ASEAN countries.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The annual event is also aimed to raise people&rsquo;s awareness of the ASEAN and promote a healthy and harmonious lifestyle under the motto of &ldquo;One Vision, One Identity and One Community,&rdquo; said Vath Chamroeun, Secretary of State at the Ministry of Education, Youth and Sports.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Moreover, he continued, the celebration is to inspire the Cambodian people, as well as those of the entire ASEAN community to participate in all kinds of sports to enhance their health, strengthen friendship, solidarity, and communication, and boost the ASEAN sports sector.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">According to Vath Chamroeun, on the same day, Indonesia also celebrated the event and invited Cambodian martial artists to participate and perform Bokator, a traditional sport unique to Cambodia.</p>', 'Admin', '2025-01-07 06:56:40', 'uploads/677cd0284c041.jpg', 1, 1, '2025-02-06 15:53:58', 55),
(8, 'FIFA ranks Cambodia 8th in ASEAN football standings', '<p>The Cambodian National Men&rsquo;s football team is ranked in eighth place out of eleven ASEAN football teams, with Thailand on top based on FIFA football rankings, which were updated on February 15.</p>\r\n<p>In eighth place Cambodian men&rsquo;s football team has made little progress and remains ranked among the bottom half of ASEAN football teams.</p>\r\n<p>The <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cambodia_national_football_team\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Cambodian men&rsquo;s football team</a>, also known as &ldquo;<em><strong>Kouprey</strong></em>&rdquo; &ndash; also nicknamed the &ldquo;forest ox&rdquo; and &ldquo;gray ox&rdquo; &ndash; currently has 931. 47 points in FIFA&rsquo;s ranking system, placing it in 8th position in ASEAN, and 179th overall in world rankings.</p>\r\n<p>The lack of improvement stems from poor performances by both senior and junior football teams in big events last year.</p>\r\n<p>The 32nd Southeast Asian Games in May in Cambodia were the first major disappointment.</p>\r\n<p>Despite great hopes of earning a medal, the Cambodia U22 national football team failed to reach the tournament&rsquo;s semi-final stage. Cambodia won only one of its three group-stage qualification matches.</p>', 'Admin', '2025-01-07 06:57:17', 'uploads/677cd04d30c37.jpg', 1, 1, '2025-02-06 07:43:25', 29),
(10, 'Sixteen kids selected to join Bati National Football School', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Following three days of try-outs, sixteen talented young footballers under fifteen from across Cambodia were selected to attend the Bati National Football and Academy Centre in Takeo province.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bati National Football School, supported by the Football Federation of Cambodia (FFC), held a recruitment session from January 16 to 18 to find new young players for training.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ouk Rina head of administration at the Bati National Football School told Khmer Times yesterday that 50 young athletes from across the kingdom took part in the try-outs.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The FFC announced the final results on Tuesday, awarding scholarships to sixteen youngsters from eleven provinces and cities. He added that students from Mondulkiri and Pailin represented the majority of all the potential footballers who were selected.</p>', 'Admin', '2025-01-07 06:59:27', 'uploads/677cd0cfe4acb.jpg', 1, 1, '2025-02-06 15:53:46', 51),
(11, 'Women’s football team ready to kick off', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Cambodia National Women&rsquo;s Football Team has spent the last several months training in China in preparation for their second appearance at the upcoming 32nd SEA Games.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The football team, along with other sports teams, was sent to train in China last September, and they will return to Cambodia in late April to compete at the games.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Keo Sarath, secretary-general of the Football Federation of Cambodia (FFC), said the Cambodian women players have been training with Chinese professional football coaches.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">He added that they have had regular friendly matches with professional and other football teams.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;This can be the best help to push them to grow technically and build more confidence on the pitch,&rdquo; he said.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;China has provided mutual technical assistance to help many Cambodian athletes, not just the football team, to prepare for the SEA Games. They (China) have provided training venues, arranged friendly matches, and covered all the basic needs. And that is why we sent them there,&rdquo; said Sarath.</p>', 'Admin', '2025-01-07 07:00:09', 'uploads/677cd0f9bcb8b.jpg', 1, 1, NULL, 9),
(12, 'GTA 6, Nintendo\'s new console and what else to watch out for in 2025 gaming', '<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\">Even if you were lucky enough to get a new console or games this Christmas, you\'ve probably got your eye on some upcoming releases.</p>\r\n<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\">And 2025 is shaping up to be a big one.</p>\r\n<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\">Most agree that 2024 was a painful year for the games industry, with tens of thousands of layoffs and worldwide studio closures.</p>\r\n<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\">There\'s a hope that things will bounce back - at least in part - next year.</p>\r\n<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\">And two huge releases in particular are likely to cut through in a big way.</p>\r\n<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\">Developer Rockstar hasn\'t revealed a huge amount about the new game beyond its dual protagonists and scenes from its fictional, Florida-inspired setting Leonida.</p>\r\n<p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\">The big question on most fans\' minds is whether the release date will slip, as has happened for previous big releases from Rockstar.</p>', 'Admin', '2025-01-07 07:03:04', 'uploads/677cd1a82b0e1.jpg', 1, 4, NULL, 7),
(14, 'Diallo seals 2-2 draw for ManU against Liverpool', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">LIVERPOOL &ndash; Amad Diallo came back to haunt Liverpool with a late equalizer that secured a 2-2 draw for Manchester United against Premier League leader Liverpool on Sunday.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The forward turned home Alejandro Garnacho&rsquo;s cross in the 80th minute at Anfield after Mohamed Salah&rsquo;s penalty had looking like giving Liverpool the win.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Diallo struck at the end of extra time as United beat Liverpool 4-3 in a dramatic FA Cup clash last season and hit a 90th-minute winner against Manchester City last month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">His goal on Sunday was only worth a point on this occasion, but it halted United&rsquo;s four-game losing run and prevented fierce rival Liverpool from opening up an eight-point lead at the top of the standings.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">United head coach Ruben Amorim, however, was still unhappy.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;It&rsquo;s a point, a deserved point, but it&rsquo;s just one point, and we should get mad. Today we should be really disappointed,&rdquo; he said.</p>', 'Admin', '2025-01-07 07:44:36', 'uploads/677cdb640e7c8.jpg', 1, 1, '2025-02-06 15:53:28', 32),
(27, 'More Possible GTA 6 Actors Discovered', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333;\">Online news has identified four more possible&nbsp;<em><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">Grand Theft Auto 6</span></strong></em>&nbsp;actors. All of them have either outright confirmed or at least hinted at being involved in&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/grand-theft-auto-6/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">GTA 6</span></em></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333;\">.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333;\">In April 2024, Rockstar reported that&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/gta-6-jason-lead-voice-actor-leak-grand-theft-auto/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Gregory Connors is the possible voice of one of the&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">GTA 6</span></em>&nbsp;protagonists</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333;\">, whom the previous leaks identified as Jason. The American actor\'s CV, which has since been pulled from the internet, stated that he\'s playing a \"lead\" role in a 2025 Rockstar title, suggesting he\'s either been cast as Jason or perhaps one of&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">GTA 6</span></em>\'s villains.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; background: white;\">A subsequent investigation by Game Rant has now yielded four more&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/gta-6-jason-lucia-lead-actors-leak-rumor-manni-perez-dylan-rourke/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">possible&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">GTA 6</span></em>&nbsp;actors</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; background: white;\">. Two of them have flat-out confirmed their involvement in Rockstar\'s much-anticipated game in their online resumes. This duo comprises Los Angeles-born actor Brandon James Somerville and American actress Stevie Dust, sometimes credited as Stevie Dutson. Somerville revealed that he plays a supporting role in&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">GTA 6</span></em>, while Dust credited herself with unspecified NPC work.</span></p>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:08:44', 'uploads/67a4a64c76436.jpg', 1, 4, '2025-02-06 15:51:20', 9),
(28, 'Apex Legends Making Anti-Cheat and Matchmaking Updates', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">In the first&nbsp;<strong><em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">Apex Legends</span></em></strong>&nbsp;developer blog of 2025, Respawn Entertainment has detailed its new armory of weapons to combat hackers and cheaters. Season 24 will bring a host of matchmaking changes aimed at making&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/apex-legends/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Apex Legends</span></em></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;a fairer battleground for all players.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Respawn Entertainment has already promised that 2025 will breathe new life into&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">Apex Legends</span></em>.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/what-to-expect-apex-legends-season-24-takeover-buffs-ttk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm;\">Season 24: Takeover launches on February 11</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, switching up the battle royale&rsquo;s long-established formula with the aim of making fights faster and more lethal. Assault characters will welcome new buffs, support characters will have their Healing Expert perk nerfed, while the implementation of Arsenals will help freshly dropped legends to dive into the fray.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"adsninja-injected-repeatable-ad-afterend\" style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Anti-cheat Updates Action taken against teaming has resulted in sanctions against 1200 accounts and the removal of 17.4 million ranked points. A brand-new \"future-proof\" machine learning model will soon be deployed to combat bots. A new Report Feedback tool is being developed to provide insights on action taken against reported cheaters. Matchmaking Updates Upcoming measures will help to ensure fair matches including: Unranked Skill Display; seeding skill values; lessening Ranked resets; queue time adjustments; and Ranked Placement matches. Teams of enemy \"Apex Bots\" may be added to low-ranking matches. Bots will not form teams with players. Testing of called-for features such as preferential matchmaking (solos vs. premades) taking place. Focus on future transparency with Apex Legends community. Acknowledging that Apex Legends has suffered a &ldquo;recent increase in bots,&rdquo; Respawn has created &ldquo;a brand-new machine learning model&rdquo; to detect both current bots and &ldquo;future variants and evolutions.&rdquo; This &ldquo;future-proof&rdquo; tool is apparently &ldquo;incredibly accurate with low false negatives&rdquo; and should already be active in-game. Respawn has also targeted teaming in Ranked game modes, where multiple opposing teams join forces to fix the match in their favor. For several months, Respawn has been &ldquo;rolling out new automated teaming detection algorithms, swifter and more severe punishments, and stripping any ill-gotten ranked points from offenders.&rdquo; Around 1200 accounts have faced bans or sanctions, and 17.4 million ranked points have been stripped from their accounts. These Anti-Cheat measures will be a welcome sight to gamers after last year\'s series of issues culminating in the public hacking of the ALGS North American regional final. The developers also stress the importance of reporting cheaters and reveal that they are looking into a system to inform players when action has been taken against a reported account, allowing gamers to see that their actions are making a difference.</span></p>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:09:48', 'uploads/67a4a68c11581.jpg', 1, 4, '2025-02-06 15:51:41', 8),
(29, 'Nintendo Hotel Partnership Rents Out Alarmo Clocks to Guests', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 36.0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">Nintendo has partnered with Universal Studios to lend Alarmo clocks to park hotel guests. The partnership gives interested Nintendo fans an opportunity to try out the Alarmo without buying it first.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>Nintendo Alarmo is one of the many surprises that Nintendo has come out with over the years. While the company is best-known for its game consoles and iconic video game franchises like Mario and Zelda, it also has a tendency to be inventive and creative, coming up with unusual releases like Nintendo Labo or Alarmo, or even unusual gaming peripherals, like the Wii Fit Board.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Hotels Offering Nintendo Alarmo for Rent</span></strong></h2>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Oriental Hotel Universal City</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The Singulari Hotel &amp; Skyspa at Universal Studios Japan</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The Park Front Hotel at Universal Studios Japan Hotel</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Kintetsu Universal City Hotel</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Keihan Universal Tower Hotel</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Universal Port Hotel</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Universal Port Vita</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Like with many Nintendo products, the Alarmo has seen some extreme demand. While it has remained available for sale in the west on the online store, it\'s only been available for Nintendo Switch Online subscribers, possibly in part to prevent excessive scalping. Starting in March 2025, <a href=\"https://gamerant.com/nintendo-alarmo-wider-release-stores-when/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm;\">Alarmo will be available in select retail stores</span></a>, so more fans will get an opportunity to try it then. Meanwhile, in Japan, the Alarmo was set to go on sale in physical stores starting in February, but has since been pushed back to an announced date.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">While some may see the Alarmo as a simple gimmick, it\'s been quite popular with some fans, and tying it into the Univeral Studios Japan park makes some sense. The park is home to Super Nintendo World, and Nintendo encourages fans to use the Alarmo to wake up to a Nintendo-filled day before they head down to the park. There\'s no announcement regarding bringing Alarmo to the western park counterparts, however. If such a collaboration happens, it might be <span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/super-nintendo-world-universal-orlando-layout/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; color: windowtext; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\">when Univeral Studios Orlando opens Super Nintendo World</span></a></span><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\">&nbsp;later in 2025.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:10:55', 'uploads/67a4a6cf01769.jpg', 1, 4, '2025-02-06 12:12:48', 6),
(30, 'Dead by Daylight Launches New Resident Evil Crossover', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Behaviour Interactive has announced&nbsp;<em><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Dead by Dayligh</span></strong></em>t&rsquo;s new crossover with&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Resident Evil</span></em>, scheduled from February 10 to February 25. This collaboration with the highly popular survival-horror franchise will introduce special gameplay, iconic&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Resident Evil</span></em>&nbsp;characters, and a new map to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/dead-by-daylight/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Dead by Daylight</span></em></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Dead by Daylight&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">offers a thrilling multiplayer experience where players face off in 4v1 matches on a map, with one player assuming the role of the killer while the other four try to find a way to escape.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/dead-by-daylight-killers-best-perks-dbd/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Dead by Daylight</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">&rsquo;s killers come from different horror genres</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, including slashers and paranormal entities, each with unique abilities to haunt the survivors. The game&rsquo;s setting and vibe have made it perfect for crossovers with other horror franchises like&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Alien</span></em>,&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Child\'s Play</span></em>,&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Ghost Face</span></em>, and&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Resident Evil</span></em>. Now, the developer has announced yet another crossover with Capcom&rsquo;s survival-horror franchise.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">Running from February 10 to February 25,&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/dead-by-daylight-resident-evil-crossover-june-2021/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Dead by Daylight&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">brings another&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Resident Evil&nbsp;</span></em>crossover</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">&nbsp;to the game. This time, the thematic additions will be featured in the 2v8 mode, where players can take on the role of&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Resident Evil</span></em>&nbsp;killers like Nemesis and the Mastermind, along with other characters and legendary outfits for players to choose from. Moreover, the 2v8 arena where players will face off is the iconic Raccoon City Police Department, one of the primary settings of&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Resident Evil 2</span></em>, which will also be added to the map rotation. Players will be pleased to know that every character in the crossover will be free to play for the duration of the event.</span></p>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:14:50', 'uploads/67a4a7bad1769.jpg', 1, 4, NULL, 13),
(31, 'Marvel Rivals Players Want Fantastic Four Movie Skins', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333;\">Marvel Rivals&nbsp;</span></strong></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333;\">players are already asking for skins based on&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">The Fantastic Four: First Steps</span></em>, which is set to hit theaters this summer. 2025 is shaping up to be an exciting year for fans of Marvel&rsquo;s First Family, as the Fantastic Four is making a huge return to screens large and small over the next few months. For starters, Mr. Fantastic and the Invisible Woman were added to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/marvel-rivals/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Marvel Rivals</span></em></a></span><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333;\">&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333;\">as playable characters on January 10, and their teammates The Thing and the Human Torch aren&rsquo;t far behind.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333;\">Meanwhile, Marvel movie fans are gearing up to see the iconic quartet make their MCU debut in&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">The Fantastic Four: First Steps</span></em>, which will arrive in theaters on July 25, 2025. A trailer for the new movie was released earlier this week, giving viewers a look at the&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/fantastic-four-first-steps-trailer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Fantastic Four&rsquo;s retro-style uniforms</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: #333333;\">, The Thing&rsquo;s more comic-accurate CGI design, and even a glimpse of the dreaded Galactus. Overall,&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">The Fantastic Four: First Steps&nbsp;</span></em>is getting plenty of buzz for its futuristic 60&rsquo;s aesthetic, and some gamers are pointing out a prime promotional opportunity for the film ahead of its highly-anticipated release.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; background: white;\">Shortly after the&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Fantastic Four: First Steps&nbsp;</span></em>trailer was released, Reddit user mighty_and_meaty suggested that NetEase Games release new&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Marvel Rivals&nbsp;</span></em>Fantastic Four skins on July 25 to pair with the movie. They note that since&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/marvel-rivals-thing-human-torch-release-date-guess-prediction/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">The Thing and the Human Torch</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; background: white;\">&nbsp;will likely be added to&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Marvel Rivals&nbsp;</span></em>by the time the movie comes out, the timing would be perfect, which is a sentiment many other users on r/marvelrivals agree with.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; background: white;\">Such a thing wouldn&rsquo;t be unprecedented for&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Marvel Rivals&nbsp;</span></em>either, as&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/marvel-rivals-insomniac-spider-man-skin-more-game-crossovers-good/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">an alternate Spider-Man skin</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333; background: white;\">&nbsp;based on his Advanced Suit 2.0 from&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Marvel&rsquo;s Spider-Man 2&nbsp;</span></em>was added when that particular game was ported to PC late last month. NetEase has also started offering exclusive rewards to promote&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Captain America: Brave New World</span></em>, including a mystery costume that could be a skin for either Captain America or the Hulk.</span></p>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:15:25', 'uploads/67a4a7dd57566.jpg', 1, 4, NULL, 15),
(32, 'Fortnite Leak Reveals All Chapter 6 Season 2 Update Release Dates', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Fortnite</span></strong></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;fans have a lot to look forward to, as the update schedule for the game has reportedly been leaked online. Despite still being several weeks away from&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Fortnite</span></em>\'s upcoming Chapter 6 Season 1 update, Epic Games has either intentionally or unintentionally revealed every date for the game\'s next content cycle, including when the next \"OG\" season launches. This news follows recent&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/fortnite/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Fortnite</span></em></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;events like the Godzilla x Kong collaboration, with plenty of fresh content on the way in the near future.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">It seems like no game is immune from leaks, especially&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Fortnite</span></em>, with collaborations, crossovers, and updates constantly being discovered online. While some of these leaks end up not happening, others, like&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/fortnite-iron-man-skin-rumor-2025/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Fortnite</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">\'s numerous Marvel collaborations</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;and the game\'s recent kaiju-themed update, were discovered months in advance. While leaks can ruin the surprise of an unannounced update, they can also build hype, with players eagerly awaiting&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Fortnite</span></em>\'s Chapter 6 Season 2 update, which has seemingly been fully revealed ahead of its official launch.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">According to&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://trello.com/b/GXLc34hk/epic-games-store-roadmap\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Epic Games\' public Trello board</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">, the schedule for every upcoming&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/fortnite-chapter-6-season-2-theme-leak/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Fortnite</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">&nbsp;Season 2 update</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">&nbsp;has been revealed. This board is where Epic shares incoming updates, bug fixes, and other news regarding&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Fortnite</span></em>\'s various modes. This new board indicates that Chapter 6 Season 2 will begin on February 21, 2025, as originally reported. However, another update will follow shortly on March 11, though its contents remain a mystery for now. Season 3 of&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Fortnite</span></em>&nbsp;OG launches on March 25, according to the table, continuing the game\'s incredibly popular \"back to basics\" experience that kicked off in 2024.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">New Fortnite Leak Reveals Update Timeline</span></h2>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Chapter 6 Season 2</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;- February 21, 2025</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">v34.10</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;- March 11, 2025</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">v34.20</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;<strong>(Fortnite OG Season 3)</strong>&nbsp;- March 25, 2025</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">v34.30</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;- April 8, 2025</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">v34.40</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;- April 22, 2025</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">v35.00</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;<strong>(Chapter 6 Season 3)</strong>&nbsp;- May 2, 2025</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Looking ahead to April, two updates are scheduled to drop, one on April 8 and one on April 22. Again, the content contained in these updates remains unknown for the time being. Assuming the table is accurate, players can expect&nbsp;<em>Fortnite</em>&nbsp;Chapter 6 Season 3 to launch on May 2. It\'s important to note these are just currently scheduled dates and are subject to change, something Epic Games itself noted on its Trello card. Epic Games is quite open about&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\"><a href=\"http://gamerant.com/fortnite-chapter-6-season-1-release-date-keyart/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Fortnite</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">&nbsp;and the game\'s various updates</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">&nbsp;and content overhauls, announcing even the smallest weapon and balance changes on its numerous social media channels.</span></p>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:16:38', 'uploads/67a4a826311d7.jpg', 1, 4, NULL, 9);
INSERT INTO `articles` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `created_at`, `image_url`, `status`, `category_id`, `updated_at`, `views`) VALUES
(33, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 Players Can Claim 2 Free Operator Skins, But There\'s a Catch', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Call of Duty: Black Ops 6&nbsp;</span></strong></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">players can now claim a free Season 2 bundle that includes 2 operator skins, 3 weapon blueprints, double XP tokens, and much more. Unfortunately, there is a catch, as this Season 2 bundle can only be claimed by&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/call-of-duty-black-ops-6/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Call of Duty: Black Ops 6</span></em></a></span><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">or&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Warzone&nbsp;</span></em>players on PlayStation 4 or PlayStation 5 who are also subscribed to the platform\'s popular subscription service, PS Plus.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Fans have been left somewhat baffled by the new PS Plus bundle, as&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Call of Duty</span></em>\'s publisher, Activision, is now owned by Sony\'s competitor, Microsoft. In October 2023,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/microsoft-acquires-activision-blizzard/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Microsoft officially completed its acquisition of Activision-Blizzard,</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;which cost a massive $68.7 billion and was the biggest acquisition in video game history. Now that Activision is under the Microsoft umbrella, many of the studio\'s titles have begun making their way to Xbox Game Pass, including the recently released&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Call of Duty: Black Ops 6</span></em>. However, despite the acquisition now being over a year old, it looks like PS Plus users are still getting some extra&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Call of Duty&nbsp;</span></em>benefits that Xbox users aren\'t.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">How To Get Free Black Ops 6 Season 2 Bundle With PS Plus</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">On February 4, a new bundle for&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/call-of-duty-black-ops-6-season-2-update-patch-notes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Call of Duty: Black Ops 6&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Season 2</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">&nbsp;made its way to the PlayStation Store. Unlike many other&nbsp;</span><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Call of Duty&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">bundles, this one can be claimed for free, but only by users who are currently subscribed to PlayStation Plus. The bundle includes 2 operator skins, 3 weapon blueprints, 2 animated emotes, a weapon charm, a weapon reticle, an emblem, a background, 2 stickers, 2 double XP tokens (1 hour), and 2 double weapon XP tokens (1 hour). To claim the bundle, subscribe to PlayStation Plus and&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\"><a href=\"https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP0002-CUSA23827_00-CODBO6PLUSPACK01\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">visit the store page for the bundle</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">&nbsp;to redeem it. The contents of the bundle will then be added to the user\'s&nbsp;</span><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Call of Duty&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">account, but it is worth noting that the terms and conditions of the bundle state that the pack is not cross-platform supported.</span></p>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:17:39', 'uploads/67a4a86309b61.jpg', 1, 4, NULL, 12),
(34, 'Dead by Daylight Releases New Update for February 2025', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Dead by Daylight</span></em></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">\'s February 2025 update has been released. With the eight-year-old competitive horror game showing no signs of slowing down,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/dead-by-daylight/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Dead by Daylight</span></em></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;puts out these regular patches to keep gameplay competitive. Especially with the amount of new Killers and perks that have been added, many old mechanics are in need of some major tweaking.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">One of the most requested changes involves The Nightmare\'s play style. Many fans believe that Freddy Krueger\'s power set was in need of a massive overhaul, especially with the diverse roster that the Killer section possesses. A&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/dead-by-daylight-the-nightmare-upcoming-changes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">January 2025&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">Dead by Daylight</span></em>&nbsp;Developer Update</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;detailed some of the new things planned for The Nightmare. And while the patch that previously went live completely renewed the character, other issues arose from it which needed further correction.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">The February 2025 Dead by Daylight tweaks some factors relating to&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/dead-by-daylight-best-builds-nightmare/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Dead by Daylight</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">\'s The Nightmare</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">&nbsp;and fixes other bugs and issues. New FX has been added when The Nightmare teleports to a healing Survivor. His Black Box add-on was also updated to block exit gates for sleeping survivors for 15 seconds after being opened. These small changes help define Freddy Krueger\'s playstyle even more. However, many other bugs involving other items and characters were also adjusted to allow for smoother gameplay.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">What\'s Been Updated in Dead by Daylight Version 8.5.1?</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Perhaps the biggest addition to the February 2025 patch is the preparation of the return of&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/dead-by-daylight-2v8-mode-what-fog-project-t-casting-frank-stone/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Dead by Daylight</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">\'s 2v8 mode</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">. While older iterations of the mode featured a small selection of playable Killers, this new version is a two-week event that will feature a tome that offers&nbsp;</span><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Resident Evil</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">-themed rewards. The said mode will be playable on February 10 and will also add The Legion, The Nemesis, and The Mastermind to the selectable characters on the Killer side. New maps such as the Raccoon City Police Department will also be available for play in 2v8.</span></p>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:18:09', 'uploads/67a4a881c53a6.jpg', 1, 4, NULL, 2),
(35, 'Pokemon TCG Pocket Leak Teases Upcoming Event', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">A new&nbsp;<em><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">Pokemon TCG Pocket</span></strong></em>&nbsp;leak has revealed an upcoming distribution event that will give rare cards to players. Like physical cards,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/pokemon-trading-card-game-pocket/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Pokemon TCG Pocket</span></em></a>&nbsp;players can get a selection of rare cards to add to their collections. To do this, they open booster packs, counting themselves lucky to pull these coveted cards or gather enough pack points to craft them.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/pokemon-tcg-pocket-ptcgp-card-raritiy-rates-diamond-star-crown-explained/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Pokemon TCG Pocket</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">&nbsp;cards are divided by rarity</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, the lowest being one-diamond and the highest being the crown cards. While diamond cards have a 100% chance of appearing from the first to the third slot of a booster pack, crown cards only have a 0.040% chance of dropping in the fourth slot and a 0.16% chance of appearing in the fifth slot. Obtaining the rarest cards in the game requires a good dose of luck and patience, but a new leak brings promising news for players.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">According to a&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.pokemon-zone.com/events/genetic-apex-presents/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">leak shared by Pokemon Zone</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">,&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">Pokemon TCG Pocket</span></em>&nbsp;will have a distribution event giving away cards of rarity four-diamond upwards. The information says that the event will start on February 27, and three packs from the&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/pokemon-tcg-pocket-all-cards-best-worst-genetic-apex/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Genetic Apex expansion</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">&nbsp;will be given away; one of Pikachu, Charizard, and Mewtwo. While this will be a great chance for players to pull coveted cards, there is a twist: only the fifth card in each pack will be rare, with the others being regular. The leak also informs that players will have until April 30 to claim the packs in their Gift Box.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Pokemon TCG Pocket Leaked Genetic Apex Expansion Distribution Event Details</span></strong></h2>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Event date: February 27 to April 30</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Rewards: a Pikachu, Charizard, and Mewtwo booster pack (guaranteed rare card in the fifth slot)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The four-diamond rarity cards in the Genetic Apex set are the regular ex, which includes popular names like Mewtwo, Blastoise, and Exeggutor. The one-star rarity are the full art rare cards, the two-star rarity are the full art ex and trainer cards, and the three-star rarity are the&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/pokemon-tcg-pocket-how-get-all-immersive-cards/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">immersive&nbsp;<em>Pokemon TCG Pocket</em>&nbsp;cards</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">. The crown rarity cards are the most difficult to see in the game and are the ex with golden backgrounds featuring Pikachu, Charizard, and Mewtwo.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">As with other leaks, players should take this information with a grain of salt as there has been no official confirmation from the developers. In the meantime, other events are officially available. One of them is giving players&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/pokemon-tcg-pocket-solo-battles-cresselia-ex-drop-event-new-promo-cards/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">new&nbsp;<em>Pokemon TCG Pocket</em>&nbsp;promo cards</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, including Cresselia ex. Like the Lapras event, this is the only way to get the ex variant of the Gen 4 Legendary. The other is the PvP event, which is giving away themed badges from the new Space-Time Smackdown expansion.</span></p>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:18:44', 'uploads/67a4a8a4d9eb9.jpg', 1, 4, NULL, 8),
(36, 'FC 25 Releases Title Update 9', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">EA Sports FC 25</span></strong></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;has recently released its Title Update 9 for all platforms. While the new update is not as large as some previous ones, it&rsquo;s still good to see Electronic Arts continuing to support&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/db/video-game/ea-sports-fc-25/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">EA Sports FC 25</span></em></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;by squashing bugs and improving the overall experience.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">EA Sports FC 25</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;is the latest entry in EA&rsquo;s famous soccer franchise and was released in September 2024. Over the months, EA has released several&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/ea-sports-fc-25-title-update-7-patch-notes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm;\">updates for&nbsp;</span><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">EA Sports FC 25</span></em></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, ranging from minor tweaks to some major changes, each time improving the game&rsquo;s quality and stability.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">Now,&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\">EA Sports FC 25</span></em>&rsquo;s new Title Update 9 has been released for all platforms. Most gamers should not expect any drastic changes in the new update, however, as it mainly fixes some glitches and makes some improvements to the game. For example, the update introduced the ability to search for OVR ranges in Club, SBCs, Rush, and Evolutions in the Ultimate Team mode, and added the ability to set Board Strictness in Live Starting Points in Career Mode.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"adsninja-injected-repeatable-ad-beforebegin\" style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Overall, Update 9 is much smaller than&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/ea-sports-fc-25-gameplay-refresh-update-patch-notes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">EA Sports FC 25</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm;\">&rsquo;s mid-season update</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, which was one of the most significant patches the popular soccer game has received so far. For instance, the update changed how attacking and defense work in&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">EA Sports FC 25</span></em>&nbsp;to make the experience feel more realistic. Also, EA has improved the quality of the teammate&rsquo;s AI while attacking to support player feedback better.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Despite EA&rsquo;s efforts to keep polishing&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">EA Sports FC 25</span></em>, it&rsquo;s fair to say that the game did not fare as well as intended. In a recent report, EA concluded that&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/dragon-age-the-veilguard-sales-underperformed-ea-expectations/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">EA Sports FC 25&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm;\">performed below expectations</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, not being able to sell as many copies as expected by the publisher.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Not everything is looking grim for the&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">EA Sports FC&nbsp;</span></em>series, however. Recent reports indicate that&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://gamerant.com/ea-tech-company-acquisition-fc-series-realism/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm;\">Electronic Arts has recently acquired TRACAB Technologies</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, a company that specializes in collecting data from real-world soccer games. With the technology provided by TRACAB, it&rsquo;s possible that future&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">EA Sports FC&nbsp;</span></em>games will have even more realistic gameplay, as the developers will have additional data about how to emulate the real-life movement of players. In any case, it&rsquo;s still unclear whether this tech will be applied to the upcoming&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">EA Sports FC 26</span></em>, which is expected to be released late in 2025, and it&rsquo;s possible that it will only affect later titles.</span></p>', 'Admin', '2025-02-06 12:19:19', 'uploads/67a4a8c7755c6.jpg', 1, 4, NULL, 5),
(37, 'Angkor Wat, the most famous Cambodian heritage site', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">Throughout Cambodia\'s</span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Culture_of_Cambodia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">&nbsp;long history</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">, religion has been a major source of cultural inspiration. Over nearly two millennia, Cambodians have developed a unique Khmer&nbsp;culture and belief system from the&nbsp;syncretism&nbsp;of indigenous animistic&nbsp;beliefs and the Indian religions of Buddhism&nbsp;and Hinduism. Indian culture and civilization, including its languages and arts reached mainland Southeast Asia&nbsp;around the 1st century A.D. It is generally believed that seafaring merchants brought Indian customs and culture to ports along the Gulf of Thailand&nbsp;and the Pacific en route to trade with China. The Kingdom of Funan&nbsp;was most probably the first Khmer state to benefit from this influx of Indian ideas. There is also French influence.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(224, 62, 45);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">History</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>The Golden Age of Cambodia was between the 9th and 14th century (the Angkor period), during which it was a powerful and prosperous empire that flourished and dominated almost all of inland Southeast Asia. However, Angkor would eventually collapse after much in-fighting between royalty and constant warring with its increasingly powerful neighbors, notably Siam and Dai Viet. Many temples from this period however, like Bayon and Angkor Wat still remain today, scattered throughout Thailand, Cambodia, Laos, and Vietnam as a reminder of the grandeur of Khmer arts and culture. Cambodia\'s unparalleled achievements in art, architectures, music, and dance during this period have had a great influence on many neighboring kingdoms, namely Thailand and Laos. The effect of Angkorian culture can still be seen today in those countries, as they share many close characteristics with current-day Cambodia.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(224, 62, 45);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">Religion</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Cambodia is predominantly Buddhist&nbsp;with 80% of the population being Theravada Buddhist,&nbsp;1% Christian and the majority of the remaining population follow Islam, atheism, or animism.</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\"><br><br><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">Buddhist nun at&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 18.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Angkor_Wat\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 194, 107);\"><em><strong>Angkor Wat</strong></em></span></span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">, Siem Reap, Cambodia. Buddhism have existed in Cambodia since the 5th century C.E. Theravada&nbsp;Buddhism has been the Cambodian state religion since the 13th century CE (excepting the Khmer Rouge period), and is currently estimated to be the faith of 90% of the population</span></p>', 'borim', '2025-02-06 14:23:09', 'uploads/67a4c5cde43e3.jpg', 1, 10, '2025-02-07 17:50:27', 7),
(38, 'Khmer New Year Culture', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">In Cambodia, Khmer New Year is the greatest traditional festival, and also the greatest national holiday.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>It is three days of festival and sometimes can be four days. Khmer New Year begins on April 13th or can begin on April 14th, depending on the &ldquo;MohaSangkran,&rdquo; which is the ancient horoscope. In fact, Khmer New Year originally began on the first day of the first month in the lunar calendar, which can be in November or the beginning of December. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">In the Angkor Era, the 13th Century, the Khmer King, either Suriyavaraman II or Jayavaraman VII, changed the New Year to the fifth month of the lunar calendar, in April by the solar calendar. 95% of Khmer population are farmers, and the period from November through March is the busiest season for Khmer farmers to reap or harvest the crops from the rice fields. Khmer people can find free time in April because there is no rain, and it is very hot, so Khmer farmers have the time to take vacation after they have worked very hard to gather the rice crops from their fields to get their income. Therefore, April is the right time for Khmer in Cambodia to celebrate New Year.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>The Khmer New Year festival originated from Bramhmanism, a part of Hinduism, which was a religion that Khmer believed in before Buddhism. Later on, Buddhism became associated with the festival and then took all the important roles in the festivity.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Usually, Khmer New Year is celebrated for three days:<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>The first day of New Year is called Moha Sangkran, and it can be described simply as the inauguration of the New Angels who come to take care of the world for a one-year period. The leader of Angels is named &ldquo;KimiteaTevi. People need to clean and decorate the house and also prepare fruits and drinks for the New Year inauguration and to welcome the New Angels at every single home.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Elderly people like to meditate or pray the Dharma at that time because they believe that any angel who comes to their houses at that time will stay with them and take care of their family for the whole year. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Actually, in the morning of the first day of New Year, most Khmer people prepare food to offer the monks at Khmer temple to get blessed. It is a great time for boys and girls to play traditional games together at the temple or any field or playground in their village because it is only at the New Year time that boys and girls are allowed to play or get together socially. Also it is a wonderful time for single people to search for the special partner to get married to in the future. In the past several decades, &ldquo;dating&rdquo; did not exist in Cambodia.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">The second day of New Year is called Wanabot, which means day of offering gifts to the parents, grandparents and elders. Usually, Khmer People like to share gifts or presents to employees and also donate money or clothes to poor people. In the evening, people go to temple to build a mountain of sand and ask the monks to give them a blessing of happiness and peace.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">The third day is called day of &ldquo;Leung Sakk;&rdquo; that means the year starts to be counted up from this day, for example it is when the year of 2000 would change and begin to be 2001.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>Traditionally, in the morning, people would go to the temple to perform the ceremony of the mountain of sand to get blessed. In the evening, to complete the New Year festival, Khmer people need to perform the last ceremony, called &ldquo;Pithi Srang Preah&rdquo;, which means giving a special bath or a special shower to Buddha statues, the monks, elders, parents and grandparents in order to apologize for any mistake done to them and to gratify them. Everyone has a wonderful time during this ceremony because it is a great opportunity for everyone, young and old, man and woman, to have much fun by spreading out water to each other.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>Khmer New Year is not just the great traditional festival for Cambodians, it can allow Cambodians to build up many unforgettable souvenirs and memories.</span></p>', 'borim', '2025-02-06 14:28:17', 'uploads/67a4c701f0ffe.jpg', 1, 10, NULL, 4);
INSERT INTO `articles` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `created_at`, `image_url`, `status`, `category_id`, `updated_at`, `views`) VALUES
(39, 'Hundreds gather for ‘bittersweet’ celebration of Hanukkah on the San Antonio River Walk', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Hundreds of people from the Jewish community on Monday gathered along the banks of the San Antonio River Walk at the Arneson River Theatre for the 27th year<strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\';\">&nbsp;</span></strong>to light the sixth candle of the menorah.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Chanukah On The River, hosted by the </span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://www.chabadsa.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Chabad Center for Jewish Life &amp; Learning</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, commemorates the sixth day of Chanukah, or Hanukkah, a family Festival of Lights that lasts eight nights. It started Christmas Day this year and leads into 2025.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">It&rsquo;s one of the first major Jewish festivals since Oct. 7, 2023, when Hamas attacked southern Israel&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/displaced-gaza-newborn-freezes-death-twin-fights-his-life-rain-floods-tents-2024-12-30/\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">killing 1,200 people and taking 251 as hostages</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">, according to Israeli tallies. The death toll in Gaza from the Israel-Hamas war has&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://apnews.com/article/israel-palestinians-hamas-war-news-12-16-2024-9f7c8f0df71dc4c97a6b31aed6e13304\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">surpassed 45,000 people</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Earlier this month, Israeli and Hamas leaders expressed hopes that talks brokered by Egypt, Qatar and the United States could lead to an agreement to halt the fighting and return 138 Israeli hostages held by Hamas, potentially opening the way to a full ceasefire agreement, according to Reuters.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">On Monday, Reuters reported that&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/displaced-gaza-newborn-freezes-death-twin-fights-his-life-rain-floods-tents-2024-12-30/\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">talk of a deal before the end of the year has faded</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;and it remains unclear how near the two sides are to an agreement.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Hanukkah celebrates the Jewish fighter&rsquo;s rise against the Syrian Greeks, who imposed idolatry on Jewish people who believed in one God, and set up their gods in their temple.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The Jewish people of Israel, or Maccabees, rededicated the temple, and a miracle happened. There was only enough oil for the menorah to last one day, but it burned for eight days.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Since then, Jewish people around the world kindle the menorah as the date that miracle happened, every night lighting one more candle.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;It&rsquo;s about the power of light, of warmth, of holiness, and it&rsquo;s about religious freedom, which is what our country stands for, that everybody can practice as they please,&rdquo; said Rabbi Chaim Block, founder of the Chabad Center for Jewish Life &amp; Learning, before the event Monday afternoon.</span></p>', 'borim', '2025-02-06 14:30:14', 'uploads/67a4c776b8718.jpg', 1, 10, NULL, 4),
(40, 'San Antonians celebrate Posadas Navideñas — the Christmas story', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Kids formed a line to take their swing at a seven-pointed pi&ntilde;ata hanging from a tree branch. When it was finally cracked open, they ran to pick up as much candy as they possibly could.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Of course they enjoyed the literal nature of breaking a pi&ntilde;ata on a random weekday night, much like any other birthday party in San Antonio. But this pi&ntilde;ata was special and the religious context explains why this tradition continues across Mexico and Hispanic communities for centuries.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">At the Rinconcito de Esperanza, about 40 people from Domesticas Unidas, the Esperanza Center and the Historic West Side Residents Association enjoyed a spread of champurrado, ponche and mole among many foods at a communal table.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">They were there to celebrate Las Posadas, a Catholic tradition in which the community reenacts the journey of Mary and Joseph to Bethlehem seeking shelter before the birth of Jesus, followed by &ldquo;breaking the seven deadly sins,&rdquo; represented by the pi&ntilde;ata.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;This is to remember the real reason we celebrate Christmas, the birth of Jesus Christ, and how his parents are very similar to many of our homeless,&rdquo; said Leticia Sanchez co-chair of the Historic West Side Residents Association, referring to the hospitality Mary and Joseph sought for the birth of Jesus.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;A lot of times, if you&rsquo;re poor, don&rsquo;t have connection or power, you&rsquo;re pushed away. But it also teaches you there is good in the world, there are good people and somebody will help,&rdquo; she said.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Sanchez has gone to many posadas growing up on the West Side.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">But over the years, it&rsquo;s changed. Oftentimes it was the local Catholic Church that has hosted neighborhood posadas. A shortage of priests at Catholic churches has impacted the number of Posada activities, Sanchez said.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">In San Antonio, Catholic Mexican families celebrate posadas with their neighbors or friends, and some churches still organize Posadas, said Ana Reyes, co-owner of Pi&ntilde;ata Time, a shop on West Commerce Street.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">It looked like carolling; Even though they sing it every year, people still needed the paper with the lyrics. And instead of Christmas decorations, colorful papel picado, string lights and several small pi&ntilde;atas adorned the patio.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">In Mexico, it&rsquo;s the same; papel picado, kids yelling, holding sticks, hitting pi&ntilde;atas, people eating an abundance of fruit and candy.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;It&rsquo;s very, very traditional,&rdquo; said Araceli Herrera, a member of Domesticas Unidas who sang among the loudest in the procession. &ldquo;It just reminds me of my country, it reminds me of my family. In Mexico, it&rsquo;s so beautiful. &hellip; We want to revive these traditions.&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif; color: #111111;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'borim', '2025-02-06 14:31:17', 'uploads/67a4c7b506744.jpg', 1, 10, NULL, 5),
(41, 'Gastronomic greats: Europe\'s top tourist cities for Michelin-starred dining', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">Plan your next trip around top-class dining thanks to these foodie-approved gems.</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">Destination dining has never been more popular. According to The Luxury Travel Book, Google searches for \"fine dining\" have surged by 49 per cent in the past year.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>Famous for its star ratings, the Michelin Guide is a great place to turn to for reliable restaurant reviews with snappy summaries.. Awarded from one to three stars, they honour top-notch food based on ingredients, technique, flavour, chef&rsquo;s personality, and consistency.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>Luckily, Europe is home to some of the World\'s most coveted Michelin-starred restaurants.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>But which European cities have the most Michelin-starred restaurants? Here\'s where you should head for your next foodie trip.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">Paris: Europe\'s gastro capital </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 36pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">Paris is home to 121 Michelin-starred restaurants and a total of 157 stars, making it Europe&rsquo;s undisputed capital of luxury dining.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>The Michelin Guide, which began awarding stars to outstanding French restaurants in 1926, played a key role in solidifying the city\'s reputation for exceptional cuisine.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>Some of the most sought-after dining spots include Le Cinq, a three-star restaurant in the Four Seasons Hotel George V, and Le Jules Verne, an emblematic restaurant on the second floor of the Eiffel Tower with sweeping views of Paris.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>For exquisite Italian dishes, reserve a spot at Il Carpacciohe, the only Michelin-starred Italian restaurant in Paris - it&rsquo;s famous for Fettuccine with black truffles.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">London: dine like a king</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 36pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">London currently has 80 Michelin-starred restaurants, making it a top contender for European destination dining. According to Michelin, the first guide to the British Isles was published in 1911 and, like the original French edition, included practical driving information for motorists.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>It ran for five editions, pausing during World War I before resuming from 1922 to 1930 under the title &lsquo;Great Britain&rsquo;. The modern &lsquo;Great Britain and Ireland&rsquo; guide, which shifted from a drivers&rsquo; handbook to a dedicated restaurant and hotel guide, was published in 1974.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>For dining in style, Sketch in London is one of the most beautiful Michelin-starred restaurants in Europe. Its lavish pink decor and modern artwork complement generous tasting and a la carte menus created by the three-Michelin-starred French master chef Pierre Gagnaire.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif;\">For an intimate dining experience, cosy up at P&eacute;trus by Gordon Ramsay in Knightsbridge. Centred around a glass-walled wine store, the small venue offers a la carte and a kitchen table\' where you can witness expert chefs at work.</span></p>', 'borim', '2025-02-06 14:32:08', 'uploads/67a4c7e86932a.jpg', 1, 10, NULL, 2),
(42, 'Holiday lights, local makers, a river parade and zines in this weekend’s Go Do That!', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">Go Do That! is a curated roundup of weekend arts and culture events from the San Antonio Report.</span></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Get a head start on the holidays with handmade crafts at the Esperanza Peace and Justice Center&rsquo;s 35th Annual&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://esperanzacenter.org/event/mercado-de-paz-peace-market-2024/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">International&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Mercado de Paz/Peace Market</span></strong></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">. The festive fun starts Friday at 10 a.m. with music by the Conjunto Heritage Taller, The Foreign Arm and Andrea &ldquo;Vocab&rdquo; Sanderson and others, and the market runs through Sunday.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">San Antonio Botanical Garden</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;offers an early glimpse of holiday lights with&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://www.sabot.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Illuminate</span></em></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, a garden full of larger-than-life light sculptures.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://www.sabot.org/illuminate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Ticketed entry times</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;run every 30 minutes from 5:30 p.m. to 9 p.m. on Friday&rsquo;s opening night.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">One hundred thousand holiday lights will illuminate the 43rd Annual&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://www.visitsanantonio.com/event/ford-holiday-river-parade-%2b-holiday-lighting/2857/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Ford Holiday River Parade</span></strong></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;on Friday from 6 p.m. to 9 p.m., with 27 illuminated floats and five entertainment floats to escort Santa and Mrs. Claus along the river. This year&rsquo;s Toy Box Adventures theme promises fun for the whole family.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://www.thesanantonioriverwalk.com/events/ford-holiday-river-parade/tickets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Tickets</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;range from $24 to $69.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Then later Friday night, head to&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Stable Hall</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;for everybody&rsquo;s favorite classic country cover band&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://www.tixr.com/groups/stablehall/events/the-texases-117442\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">The Texases</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">. They rocked the joint during the grand opening concert in January, so come prepared to dance. Doors at 7 p.m.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">A Saturday song swap? Head to&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dellviewmusicsatx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; font-weight: normal; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Dellview Music Center</span></a></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;at Noon to hear a bevy of songsters including&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://sanantonioreport.org/wendy-b-brandon-padier-garrett-t-capps-juneteenth-new-album/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Brandon Padier</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://sanantonioreport.org/la-semana-alegre-music-festival-2024-civic-park-hemisfair-san-antonio/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Chavela</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;and many more exchanging self-penned tunes. Wander a local vendors market and partake of food and drink until 5 p.m., all part of a fundraiser to benefit Dellview&rsquo;s after school music clubs.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Sunday is&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">San Antonio Zine Fest</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">. Sociedad Fraternal Cruz Blanca on the West Side hosts this&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/DCcAPcNRD8O/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">annual event for zinesters</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;to display their wares and find community. Free for all ages from 10 a.m. to 5 p.m.</span></p>', 'Panha', '2025-02-06 14:33:48', 'uploads/67a4c84c661ee.jpg', 1, 10, NULL, 14),
(43, 'Alamo Beer Company files for bankruptcy amid industry struggles', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">Alamo Beer Company, one of San Antonio&rsquo;s most well-known craft breweries, has filed for Chapter 11 bankruptcy in the Western District of Texas.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Founded by Eugene Simor in 1997, the company began showing signs of struggles in the fall. Pointing to rising operational costs and declining sales, Simor told the&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://www.expressnews.com/business/article/alamo-beer-co-brewery-san-antonio-east-side-19744825.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Express-News</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;that, while the brewery has the capacity to produce 40,000 barrels annually, it was only producing about 7,600 barrels &mdash; less than 20% of its potential.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Chapter 11 bankruptcy allows a company to reorganize its finances and attempt to return to profitability while keeping business operations running. The filing reveals that the company&rsquo;s estimated value and potential liabilities are both in the range of $1 million up to $10 million.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Alamo Beer has taken steps to stay afloat, including a merger with local brewery Viva Beer and acquiring Austin-based ShotGun Seltzer. The company has also explored selling part of its Eastside property, including a two-acre parking lot listed for $1.5 million.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Alamo Beer&rsquo;s bankruptcy filing is the latest sign of trouble in San Antonio&rsquo;s brewing scene, where several breweries &mdash;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://sanantonioreport.org/weathered-souls-brewery-closes-san-antonio-marcus-baskerville-black-owned/\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">including Weathered Souls</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, Busted Sandal and Second Pitch &mdash; have closed due to financial challenges.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The industry has faced rising labor and ingredient costs, along with shifts in consumer habits and increasing competition. Overall, U.S. beer production and imports&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://www.brewersassociation.org/statistics-and-data/national-beer-stats/\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">were down</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;5% in 2023, while craft brewer volume sales declined by 1%.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://nbwa.org/resources/covid-19s-impact-on-the-beer-industry/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Data from the National Beer Wholesalers Association</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;shows the craft beer trade in the U.S. was dramatically impacted by the pandemic, with sales for the majority of breweries plummeting.</span></p>', 'Panha', '2025-02-06 14:35:01', 'uploads/67a4c895bd13c.jpg', 1, 11, NULL, 7),
(44, 'USAA CEO Wayne Peacock reflects on a changing world', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">USAA&rsquo;s outgoing President and CEO Wayne Peacock has a lot more than golf and beach vacations on his mind these days as he heads into retirement this spring.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Peacock, who took up the helm of the Fortune 500 banking and insurance giant in 2020 as its first civilian CEO, sat down with former Speaker of the Texas House Joe Straus earlier this week for a fireside chat hosted by the World Affairs Council of San Antonio to discuss closing out his tenure.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">In a rapidly changing world where natural disasters and global inflation are becoming the norm, Peacock said he hopes USAA can continue to be a pillar of hope and strength to the 13.5 million global members who depend on the company.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;We have made investments to ensure that USAA remains relevant for the future,&rdquo; he said, noting that the board has already&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://sanantonioreport.org/usaa-announces-juan-c-andrade-as-next-president-ceo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">selected Juan Andrade</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;as his successor.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Like many insurance companies today, USAA is facing unprecedented times that include economic challenges such as rising interest rates and geopolitical risks, he said. While the company can&rsquo;t tackle these issues alone, it can aim to make them less difficult for their members, Peacock said.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">He pointed to USAA&rsquo;s recent response to the California wildfires as an example. Since the wildfires broke out on Jan. 7, USAA has processed more than 6,000 claims in the Los Angeles area largely through using satellite and drone imagery to help assess damage and expedite claim payments, Peacock said.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;We were the first on the ground and the first to get money into our members&rsquo; hands,&rdquo; Peacock said. About 1,000 of those claims were for homes that were completely destroyed, he said.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Peacock said he believes that the way USAA has embraced technology, including artificial intelligence, will only continue to help the company grow into the future.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;No matter what we think about the pace behind us, the pace in front of us is going to move much more quickly,&rdquo; he said.</span></p>', 'Panha', '2025-02-06 14:35:33', 'uploads/67a4c8b52b400.jpg', 1, 11, NULL, 9),
(45, 'New Spurs arena estimated to cost $1B, funded in part by potential hotel tax increase', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">A proposed downtown arena for the San Antonio Spurs basketball team is expected to cost roughly $1 billion, funded in part by a potential increase to the county&rsquo;s hotel occupancy tax, according to a discussion among Bexar County leaders on Tuesday.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The county&rsquo;s financial analysts say Bexar County&rsquo;s venue tax &mdash; considered one of the most likely source of public funds &mdash;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://sanantonioreport.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bexar-county-venue-tax.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">could provide about $400 million</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, according to County Manager David Smith.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">If voters approve an increase to the hotel occupancy tax that could be stretched to about $448 million &mdash; money that&rsquo;s expected to help fund the arena, as well as other major upgrades to keep the existing Frost Bank Center in use.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The estimates come as county leaders are seeking to put hard numbers behind a potential public-private partnership that&rsquo;s been closely-guarded.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">They&rsquo;re also considering a number of other uses for that money outside of a Spurs arena, such a renovations to both the Frost Bank Center and Freeman Coliseum.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;This was my effort to be open and transparent, to start letting the public know, this is your tax money,&rdquo; Bexar County Judge Peter Sakai said of the venue tax presentation. &ldquo;&hellip; I&rsquo;m not committed to a tax increase at this time.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The Spurs&rsquo; owners have been working behind the scenes with city officials on a&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://sanantonioreport.org/downtown-san-antonio-entertainment-district-unveiled-with-new-spurs-arena/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">landscape-changing entertainment district</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;for more than a year &mdash; and even pushed the county to ask voters for money to fund the arena in the May municipal election &mdash; all without ever disclosing the projected cost and revenue sources.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">That lack of transparency ultimately cost the team a crucial deadline when lining up the funding, as county leaders said they were uncomfortable asking voters to put money forward without seeking the full picture of the project&rsquo;s funding.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;For all practical purposes, the May election has come and gone,&rdquo; Sakai said Tuesday.</span></p>', 'Panha', '2025-02-06 14:36:01', 'uploads/67a4c8d158fc7.jpg', 1, 11, NULL, 15),
(46, 'Bexar County approves $2M in incentives for global manufacturer of recyclable panels made of ag waste', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">Bexar County Commissioners on Tuesday approved an economic development package worth over $2.2 million for a manufacturer planning to build its first U.S. plant in the southeast part of the county.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">ECOR Global, a manufacturer with facilities in Serbia and the Netherlands, makes recyclable commercial panels using agricultural waste fiber. The company plans to invest at least $160 million in a 300,000-square-foot facility located in Elmendorf and hire 160 workers with a base hourly salary of $20.54, according to county documents.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;We came here because our first clients in the United States are European companies that have facilities in Texas,&rdquo; said Steven Mueller, senior vice president for development at ECOR.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The plant will cost closer to $200 million to build, up from the $160 million estimated a few months ago.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">In exchange for the commitment to bring the factory and jobs to the county, commissioners approved a 10-year, 50% property tax abatement for ECOR, an incentive package valued at $2,210,648.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">ECOR produces hardboard sheets ranging in thicknesses out of agricultural waste such as corn and cotton stocks, and recycled paper and cardboard.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">More than a million tons of waste fiber is available locally every year from corn and cotton stalks, gin wastes, rice straw and wheat, which is more than five times the volume needed for the plant.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;We can use all that material and pay the farmers for it,&rdquo; Mueller said.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The process also does not rely on trees, chemicals or toxic glues, but instead on a combination of heat, pressure and recycled water to create a controlled chemical reaction, according to the company&rsquo;s website.</span></p>', 'Panha', '2025-02-06 14:36:34', 'uploads/67a4c8f24167b.jpg', 1, 11, NULL, 5);
INSERT INTO `articles` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `created_at`, `image_url`, `status`, `category_id`, `updated_at`, `views`) VALUES
(47, 'Elon Musk’s Boring Company ‘ghosted’ San Antonio on transit tunnel plan', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">It&rsquo;s been three years since a Bexar County agency gave the nod for an underground tunnel between the airport and downtown San Antonio.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">It now appears those plans have been tanked, but not by the controversy over cost and environmental impact that ensued.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The Boring Company is a tunneling company owned by Elon Musk, the businessman behind Tesla and SpaceX who has emerged as a political figure with a role in the Trump administration&rsquo;s Department of Government Efficiency.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">In 2021, the&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://www.bexar.org/339/Alamo-Regional-Mobility-Authority\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Alamo Regional Mobility Authority</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, an agency tasked with improving transportation in Bexar County, released a request for information (RFI) inviting revenue-generating transit proposals.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://sanantonioreport.org/tunnels-and-tracks-airport-downtown-project-advances/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The Boring Company and four others responded</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">; three proposals were advanced for consideration.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Boring&rsquo;s proposal was a rideshare system using Tesla&rsquo;s electric-powered cars in a tunnel 30 feet below ground and ferrying passengers the 9 miles between the airport and downtown.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The total estimated cost was between $247 million and $289 million, with estimated revenue to the RMA that was expected to come in at $25 million a year.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Boring said it would foot the entire $27 million to $45 million bill for the first phase of the project, while the other&nbsp;proposals relied heavily on federal subsidies.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The other bids included one that employed an autonomous bus using a combination of elevated and underground tracks; one that pitched an autonomous tram running along the U.S. Hwy. 281 right-of-way, and another that used a system of at-grade or elevated travel lanes running along McCullough Avenue.<strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\';\">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">A plan offered by TriTrack Motors called for spending $24 million to build an elevated track for three-wheeled autonomous vehicles that could travel at up to 180 mph.</span></p>', 'Panha', '2025-02-06 14:37:04', 'uploads/67a4c9109a0e7.jpg', 1, 11, NULL, 13),
(48, 'Broadway East project near the Pearl hopes to bring in luxury brands like Gucci, Rolex', '<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">He Pearl is about to get a new neighbor and what that looks like is finally coming into focus.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The owners of a plot of land on Broadway Street, long-vacant in one of San Antonio&rsquo;s fastest-growing corridors, revealed their plans recently for a required review by the city&rsquo;s Historic and Design Review Commission (HDRC).&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">On Wednesday, the commission granted conceptual approval to the plans. But they asked the applicant to consider relocating a historic house to property they own across the street &mdash; versus another neighborhood &mdash; and to create shade for pedestrians along Broadway and to return for a design review meeting after some of these stipulations are met.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">enderings show a dense 3.4-acre shopping mecca of luxury brands that the developers are calling Broadway East San Antonio (BESA), a counterpart to the dining-centric development at the former brewery.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;Silver Ventures has developed a fantastic project for the city and done an excellent job of curating local retail and restaurants for the Pearl,&rdquo; said Benjamin Dreszer, president and partner of Fulcrum Development. &ldquo;Because of the overall success of their project and the impact it has had on the city, national and regional tenants would like to be as close to the Pearl as possible.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The project would be built on a block of individual parcels bounded by Broadway Street to the west, Casa Blanca Street to the south, North Alamo Street to the east and the 1800 Broadway apartments to the north, according to the package prepared for HDRC.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Stores could include luxury home furnishings, high-end fashion stores such as Gucci, Peter Millar and Rolex, wellness and beauty the likes of Chanel, and upmarket heritage brands like Lucchese and Ralph Lauren, according to a&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://shopcompanies.com/sites/default/files/BESA%20District.2_1.pdf\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">sales brochure</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;Broadway East provides those tenants the opportunity to literally be at the Pearl&rsquo;s front door,&rdquo; Dreszer said.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The first phase of the project will feature 175,000 square feet of retail space, according to the brochure, and the second phase will feature mixed-use spaces, including office, retail, hospitality and additional retail.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Dreszer said he expects the project to be completed in less than two years from the start of construction and the first retail tenants to open their doors in late 2027.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The BESA property is situated inside of an area designated River Improvement Overlay (RIO)-2, which extends from Highway 281 North to Lexington Avenue in downtown San Antonio.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">In August 2022, the owners sought and obtained from the city a RIO&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://sanantonioreport.org/broadway-hdrc-panel-building-height-zoning/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Development Node</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;Zoning Overlay on the property.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The development node allows the developer to design buildings with no setbacks from all property lines and exceed the building height from 10 stories to 15.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Other development nodes in the area include the eight-story Oxbow office building developed by Silver Ventures and a 12-story tower that serves as Credit Human headquarters.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Another&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://sanantonioreport.org/board-to-graystreet-on-20-story-hotel-office-tower-go-for-it/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">development node in the vicinity</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">, approved in 2018, sits just south of those properties at 1611 Broadway, and is where GrayStreet had once touted plans to build a 20-story hotel tower.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">In 2020, GrayStreet&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://sanantonioreport.org/restoring-the-light-long-idle-newspaper-building-nears-return/\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">completed its $47 million renovation</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;of the former San Antonio Light newspaper building at 420 Broadway St. into mixed-use office and retail space.</span></p>', 'Panha', '2025-02-06 14:37:51', 'uploads/67a4c93f402e3.png', 1, 11, NULL, 42),
(49, 'County leaders approve $5M in funding for JCB to extend proposed Kelly Parkway', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">Bexar County commissioners on Tuesday approved a multi-million-dollar grant for the equipment maker JCB to make public infrastructure improvements in support of its plant under construction on the South Side.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The funding is part of an economic development incentive package from Bexar County, San Antonio and state leaders&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://sanantonioreport.org/bexar-county-san-antonio-incentive-agreement-to-lure-jcb-manufacturing-plant-south-side/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">worth almost $32 million</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;that last year lured the Great Britain-based construction equipment manufacturer to San Antonio.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The agreement with Bexar County called for a grant of up to $5 million for the Kelly Parkway Extension project and installing a water main extension along Applewhite Road.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Commissioners voted for the highest possible value in approving the grant.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">In April, City Council approved tax abatements and incentives worth $13.74 million. Bexar County provided a package valued at roughly $12 million.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">JCB is the world&rsquo;s largest privately-owned construction and agricultural equipment maker and&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://sanantonioreport.org/jcb-san-antonio-groundbreaking-southside-manufacturing-plant/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">broke ground on the factory</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;in June. The company is building a 72,000-square-foot facility at a 400-acre site at Palo Alto Road and South Zarzamora Street on the South Side.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The plant will employ 1,500 workers within five years, jobs that pay an hourly wage of at least $20.54, which is the minimum set by the city as a qualification for economic development incentives.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Openings for skilled trades and engineering jobs will be posted&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\"><a href=\"https://us241.dayforcehcm.com/CandidatePortal/en-US/jcb/Site/CANDIDATEPORTAL?l=58\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">to the JCB website</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&nbsp;and recruiting will start in mid-2025, said a spokeswoman, who has not yet commented regarding the grant.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;This facility is part of JCB&rsquo;s $500 million commitment to the region and reflects our focus on supporting the growing demand for advanced construction equipment in North America,&rdquo; according to a previous statement from JCB shared by spokeswoman Arielle Windham. &ldquo;The state-of-the-art facility will focus on producing telescopic handlers and mobile elevating work platforms, with initial production slated to begin by mid-2026.&rdquo;</span></p>', 'Panha', '2025-02-06 14:38:16', 'uploads/67a4c95872a95.jpg', 1, 11, NULL, 48),
(50, 'Cryptocurrency mining firm moves headquarters from Canada to San Antonio', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">HIVE Digital, a publicly traded cryptocurrency mining firm, announced this week that it will relocate its headquarters from Vancouver to San Antonio, citing support from President-elect Donald Trump&rsquo;s administration for the crypto industry&rsquo;s growth as a key factor in the decision.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The company described the move as a strategic response to Trump&rsquo;s re-election, highlighting the administration&rsquo;s pro-Bitcoin stance and its focus on innovation and regulatory frameworks for the cryptocurrency ecosystem.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;The United States offers a competitive and business-friendly regulatory environment, along with access to capital markets,&rdquo; the company said. &ldquo;Texas, in particular, stands out for its supportive business climate, energy infrastructure, and skilled workforce.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The shift underscores the growing interest in cryptocurrency and related businesses.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Cryptocurrency is a digital form of currency, such as Bitcoin, that operates independently of a central authority or government. Bitcoin lets people send money directly to each other without a bank, using a secure technology called blockchain.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Following China&rsquo;s 2021 ban on crypto mining, U.S. mining activity surged, with Texas emerging as the top destination for large-scale operations.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Cryptomining is the process of using computer power to solve complex mathematical problems in order to validate transactions and secure a cryptocurrency network, earning new coins as a reward.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">However, the rise of cryptomining in Texas has also sparked concerns. Critics argue that industrial-scale Bitcoin mining is driving up energy prices and straining the state&rsquo;s power grid. Local politicians have raised alarms about the environmental impact and potential risks to the state&rsquo;s energy infrastructure.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 24pt 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">In addition to its favorable regulatory environment, HIVE emphasized the U.S. is a hub for funding opportunities.</span></p>', 'Panha', '2025-02-06 14:38:40', 'uploads/67a4c9709945a.jpg', 1, 11, NULL, 106),
(53, 'Cuban Embassy pays courtesy visit to Phnom Penh Administration to strengthen diplomatic relations and foster cooperation', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">On Thursday, Milena Caridad Zaldivar Piedra, Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of the Republic of Cuba to Cambodia, paid a courtesy call on Phnom Penh&rsquo;s Governor Khuong Sreng at Phnom Penh City Hall.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khuong Sreng expressed gratitude on behalf of the Republic of Cuba, an old friend, for its support of Cambodia in the fields of health, education, and agriculture since the establishment of diplomatic relations between Cambodia and Cuba in 1979. He noted that during the 1980s, particularly, Cuba&rsquo;s assistance to Cambodia after liberation from the genocidal Pol Pot regime had been significant. He added that Cuba has greatly contributed to Cambodia&rsquo;s post-war development.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">He stated that the diplomatic ties established by Samdech Norodom Sihanouk and Fidel Castro have ensured ongoing relations between Cambodia and Cuba since ancient times. However, after Cambodia&rsquo;s liberation from the Pol Pot regime, Hun Sen, who was Cambodia&rsquo;s diplomatic guide at the time, also forged relations with numerous other countries.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">He remarked that Cuba was among the nations establishing diplomatic ties with the People&rsquo;s Republic of Cambodia during that period.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">He mentioned a Cambodian slogan that says, &ldquo;help each other in times of poverty,&rdquo; emphasising that when Cambodia faced hardship, Cuba provided various forms of free aid.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">He informed the Cuban Ambassador of the Phnom Penh authorities&rsquo; readiness to assist with any necessary work, particularly regarding the diplomatic mission in Phnom Penh, and to ensure the safety of the Cuban Embassy there.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In response, Ambassador Milena Caridad Saldivar Piedra emphasised the robust diplomatic ties between Cuba and Cambodia, pledging to uphold the values of friendship and solidarity, and to further enhance their relations.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">She requested the Phnom Penh administration to explore the possibility of locating a school that was formerly known as the Cuban School, which would enable the Cuban embassy to visit and plant a tree as a memorial to symbolise the friendship between Cuba and Cambodia.</p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-07 14:26:15', 'uploads/67a68742d0518.jpg', 1, 12, '2025-02-07 22:20:50', 18),
(55, 'Angelina Jolie: I consider Cambodia as my home', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">Hollywood star Angelina Jolie &ndash; who became a Cambodian citizen in 2005 &ndash; has stated in a recent interview that she considers Cambodia as her home.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">the&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Tomb Raider</span></em>&nbsp;star was asked where she considered was her home.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;In my heart, Cambodia,&rdquo; Jolie answered. &ldquo;My first trip was&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Tomb Raider</span></em>, where you saw me hanging upside down.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;I learned something about life. I think about my life and the amount of things I almost didn&rsquo;t do, almost missed, that would&rsquo;ve changed the course of my life. I said no to&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">Tomb Raider</span></em>&nbsp;when I was first called.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">While Tomb Raider may have brought her there, the Oscar winner formed a deep connection with the Southeast Asian country by adopting her first child, Maddox, a year after the film was released.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; background: white; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Jolie credits her son Maddox, now 23, for encouraging her to make the Netflix film&nbsp;<em><span style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">First They Killed My Father</span></em>, which takes place in her son&rsquo;s home country.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The drama, directed by Jolie, is based on her friend Loung Ung&rsquo;s memoir about surviving the Khmer Rouge genocide in Cambodia.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Jolie previously told PEOPLE that her son &ldquo;goes back and forth [to Cambodia] a lot, but this would be over four months of just being in the country, really reading, listening, learning and absorbing all things about his culture and country [including] the very, very dark parts.&rdquo;</span></p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:18:53', 'uploads/67a6b0fd84313.jpg', 1, 12, NULL, 2),
(56, 'Phnom Penh authorities ask law enforcement agencies and owners of condos, apartments, hotels, guesthouse to cooperate in managing the presence of foreigners.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; color: black; background: white;\">His Excellency Hun Surithy, Deputy Governor of Phnom Penh, has requested that authorities, forces, and owners of condos, apartments, hotels, guesthouses, and rental houses work together closely to control the presence of foreigners by ensuring that all foreigners residing in Phnom Penh are legally residing.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; color: black;\">This request by His Excellency Hun Surithy was made while presiding over a meeting on the promotion of work to control the presence of foreigners to owners and managers of condos, apartments, hotels, guesthouses, and rental houses in Phnom Penh on the afternoon of February 6, 2025, at Phnom Penh City Hall.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; color: black;\">His Excellency Hun Surithy stated that the purpose of inviting owners and managers of condos, apartments, hotels, guesthouses, and rental houses to this meeting is to disseminate the content of the management of the presence of foreigners to ensure that foreigners staying at business locations are all legally residing, have no crimes, and are not fleeing to hide.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; color: black;\">He added that owners must avoid being accused of being complicit in covering up crimes or hiding foreigners illegally residing in Cambodia.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; color: black;\">His Excellency continued: &ldquo;The Phnom Penh authorities truly support your business opening, but we also do not want to see you engaging in illegal activities, such as renting business premises to open as illegal gambling venues or harboring illegal foreigners.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; color: black;\">In order for owners and managers of condos, apartments, hotels, guesthouses, and rental houses to be exempt from legal penalties when foreigners come to rent, they must report to the FPCS system, which is a data management system for foreigners throughout Cambodia.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; color: black;\">Complete administrative procedures by getting a stamp from the commune with a clear contract stating how many foreigners are staying, how many days, months, etc.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; color: black;\">If owners do not follow the instructions above, when there is a problem, they may face legal action</span></p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:20:44', 'uploads/67a6b16ce5b97.jpg', 1, 12, NULL, 2),
(57, '2 brothers die in smash', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #323232; background: white;\">A family is in mourning after 2 brothers died after their moto was hit by a truck yesterday.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #323232; background: white;\">The traffic accident occurred at 6:30 a.m. on February 6, 2025, along the highway in Puk Chhmar village, Anlong Vil commune, Sangke district, Battambang province.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #323232;\">Residents said that the traffic accident occurred between a Wave motorcycle, driven by a 32-year-old man, and his 12-year-old brother, traveling from south to north and A large white cargo truck, driven by a man at high speed.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #323232;\">The truck hit the motorcycle head-on, causing the two brothers to die on the spot.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #323232;\">The truck then hit a resident&rsquo;s house and overturned.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #323232;\">After the incident, the police arrived at the scene and took the body to the relatives for burial.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #323232;\">The two vehicles were taken into custody by the provincial traffic police for further procedures.</span></p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:21:22', 'uploads/67a6b19235aa1.jpg', 1, 12, NULL, 1),
(58, 'Louts attack Phnom Penh monks', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">Police are seeking 3 yobs who beat monks at a Phnom Penh pagoda.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">This shocking incident occurred at 1:00 am on February 6, 2025, in the compound of Wat Sambour Meas, Mal Village, Dangkor Sangkat, Dangkor District.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">According to the monk&rsquo;s statement, the victim was monitoring a burning tree.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Suddenly, a group of three teenagers riding an unmarked motorbike arrived at the temple.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">They shouted at the monk, &ldquo;Come closer, please.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The teenagers then attacked the monk and, when 2 other monks came to intervene, the louts also attacked them.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The teenagers then fled the scene.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">A short while later, two military police officers arrived at the scene and told the three monks to wait until morning to file a complaint at the Dangkor District Military Police Station.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">When morning came, the three monks went to file a complaint with the Dangkor District Military Police Station so that the Military Police could investigate and punish the group of young people according to the law.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">After receiving the complaint from the three monks, the military police arrived at the Sambour Meas Temple compound and searched for one suspect.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">They took him to the Dangkor District Military Police Base for questioning.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The military police are currently searching for the other two suspects who are on the run.</span></p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:21:48', 'uploads/67a6b1ac45993.jpg', 1, 12, NULL, 1),
(59, 'Clement days forecast for Cambodia', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #323232; background: white;\">The Ministry of Water Resources and Meteorology has issued a notification on weather conditions in Cambodia from the 7th of February to 9th of February.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #323232;\">Northeast monsoon with low pressure covers the South China Sea, Lower Mekong Basin and the Kingdom of Cambodia.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #323232;\">This situation will make: From 7 to 9 February 2025</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #323232;\">1. Lowland: Minimum average temperature 19 &deg; C and maximum average temperature 32 &deg; C. Winds from the northeast and north have an average speed of 3 meters per second.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #323232;\">2. Upland: Minimum average temperature 18 &deg; C and maximum average temperature 32 &deg; C. Winds from the northeast and north have an average speed of 3 meters per second.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #323232; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">3- Coastal area: &ndash; Minimum average temperature 20 &deg; C and maximum average temperature 32 &deg; C. Winds from the northeast and east average 2 meters per second. Wave heights have a minimum average height of 0.25 meters and a maximum average height of 0.5 meters.</span></p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:22:26', 'uploads/67a6b1d265af6.jpg', 1, 12, NULL, 1);
INSERT INTO `articles` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `created_at`, `image_url`, `status`, `category_id`, `updated_at`, `views`) VALUES
(60, 'China will not allow any deliberate vilification against China-Cambodia friendship, says FM spokesperson', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">A Chinese foreign ministry spokesperson, Guo Jiakun,stated yesterday that China will not permit any intentional vilification of the China-Cambodia friendship, and any purveyor of rumours will bear legal responsibility and consequences.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">A handful of we-media accounts have recently published unfounded claims suggesting that Cambodian leaders are taking sides between China and the United States and that significant cooperation projects between China and Cambodia are stalling.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">In response to a related enquiry, Guo indicated at a press briefing that these comments regarding Cambodia are purely baseless smear campaigns and deliberate vilification.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">China and Cambodia are steadfast friends, supporting one another through both struggles and successes. This time-honoured friendship was nurtured by the previous generations of leaders from both countries and has withstood the challenges of the changing international landscape. It aligns with the fundamental interests of both nations and their peoples, possesses strong vibrancy and promising developmental prospects, and cannot be weakened or undermined by any force, Guo stated.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">China and Cambodia regard each other as the most trustworthy friends and reliable partners, consistently supporting each other&rsquo;s core interests. Guo emphasised that this characteristic defines China-Cambodia relations and serves as the foundation of their long-standing friendship.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The effort to build a China-Cambodia community with a shared future has yielded tangible benefits for both peoples.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">China has remained Cambodia&rsquo;s largest source of foreign investment and its biggest trading partner for consecutive years. Bilateral trade has nearly quadrupled in the past decade, noted Guo. Cambodian leaders have repeatedly asserted that China is Cambodia&rsquo;s most trusted friend and that the friendship with China is a firm political consensus within the Cambodian government, political parties, and the Cambodian populace.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Currently, China and Cambodia are steering the high-quality development of their bilateral relations through a framework of high-level mutual trust. They continue to enhance the &ldquo;Diamond Hexagon&rdquo; cooperation framework, devise cooperation plans for the Industrial Development Corridor and the &ldquo;Fish and Rice Corridor,&rdquo; advance the implementation of priority cooperation projects, facilitate each other&rsquo;s modernisation processes, deliver more substantial benefits to both peoples and provide greater stability and certainty in addressing international and regional challenges, Guo noted.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">&ldquo;We firmly believe that the unbreakable friendship between China and Cambodia will remain free from disruptions. We will not tolerate any intentional vilification of our friendship, and any rumour-monger will face legal responsibility and consequences,&rdquo; Guo asserted.</span></p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:23:16', 'uploads/67a6b204b2e46.jpg', 1, 12, NULL, 1),
(61, 'No scientific evidence indicates that mobile phone antennas pose a risk to human health, says PM', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">Prime Minister Hun Manet appealed to the public not to worry about the health risks associated with mobile phone antennas, as studies conducted by the World Health Organization (WHO) indicate that there is no scientific evidence showing that mobile phone antennas adversely affect citizens&rsquo; health. If such health risks were present, all countries, particularly developed ones, would cease using mobile phone services.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The Premier spoke on Thursday at the Ministry of Post and Telecommunications&rsquo; conference, which reviewed the work from 2020 to 2024 on the journey towards digital transformation, outlining future directions.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The Prime Minister emphasised, &ldquo;I have heard claims that being too close to a mobile phone can cause cancer or that prolonged phone use may lead to cancer. However, various studies suggest that it is generally safe. The ministry has also monitored this issue. Naturally, there is some radiation&mdash;natural stones emit radiation too. The difference lies in the amount, whether it is more or less, but it is present in phone systems as well.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;Nevertheless, the placement of mobile antennas must be carefully considered, just like any other infrastructure development. We must take ecological factors into account, integrating them into urban planning rather than installing antennas haphazardly. That is why we have a Master Plan. Adjustments are costly and time-consuming, so careful planning is essential, especially in certain towns where services remain weak, and internet or phone connections are unreliable,&rdquo; he added.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">On this occasion, the Premier also urged service providers to address the aforementioned issues and enhance the reliability of network systems. </span></p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:23:43', 'uploads/67a6b21fe96f2.jpg', 1, 12, NULL, 0),
(62, 'PP installs road dividers on Hun Sen Bvd for safety', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">The Phnom Penh Municipal Administration have started installing road dividers, traffic lanes and extra road signs along Hun Sen Boulevard, aiming to reduce traffic accidents and improve safety for road users.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The Municipal Administration began installing the dividers, lanes and signs along Hun Sen Boulevard, also known as the 60-metre road, in Chak Angkre Krom commune, Meanchey district yesterday.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The work is being carried out by the Public Works and Transport Department of Phnom Penh.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Dor Samphors, Director of the Administration and Spokeswoman at Phnom Penh Municipality Administration, said yesterday that the installation of concrete and steel barricades in the middle of the road was part of the City Hall&rsquo;s efforts to reduce traffic accidents.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">She said that installation of the dividers will start at the Morodok Techo flyover and continue to the traffic lights at the intersection of National Road 2 and Hun Neang Boulevard in Kandal province.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;The 60-metre road has recently had frequent traffic accidents, claiming the lives of many people and causing tragedy for the people. People using the road have requested authorities to install the concrete and steel barriers,&rdquo; Samphors said yesterday.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;The authorities have taken measures to prevent further traffic accidents,&rdquo; she said, adding that &ldquo;After receiving permission for the installation of the roads dividers from Prime Minister Hun Manet, the City Hall started work along the middle of the 60-metre road.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Samphors said that infrastructure is not the cause of road accidents, but rather vehicle users who are drunk or careless.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">&ldquo;To prevent future road accidents, authorities urge people to respect traffic laws and avoid driving after drinking,&rdquo; she said.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Keo Bunthoeun, an official from the Public Works and Transport Department in Phnom Penh, said that the 60-metre road has also been divided into lanes for cars and motorcycles, and additional road signs have been installed.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: DaunPenh; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">He said that the speed limit from the Mercedes showroom to the Morodok Techo flyover is 40 kmh, while from National Road 2 to the Mercedes showroom is 60 kmh.</span></p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:24:13', 'uploads/67a6b23d357ea.jpg', 1, 12, NULL, 2),
(63, 'Svay Rieng wrap up ACC group stage matches with 4-2 win', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">Preah Khan Reach Svay Rieng FC defeated Myanmar&rsquo;s Shan United 4-2 in the last group stage match of the ASEAN Club Championship (ACC) on Wednesday night at the National Olympic Stadium in Phnom Penh.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">Svay Rieng FC and Shan United delivered their final performances in the ASEAN Club Championship. Both teams were already eliminated from the tournament, therefore the battle was for pride rather than progression.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">Ye Yint Aung, the away team&rsquo;s midfielder, scored the game&rsquo;s opening goal in just seven minutes by placing the ball in the top left corner. Sang Hankhun, the Svay Rieng goalkeeper who made his debut with the club in the international football tournament in place of first-choice Vireak Dara, attempted to save but the ball went in too quickly.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">In the 15th minute, Svay Rieng leveled through Brazilian attacker Cristian Roque, who was inside the penalty box and then used his left foot to put the ball in the back of the net after collecting a through-in ball from midfielder Min Ratanak. Five minutes later from the home team&rsquo;s first goal, midfielder Ratanak provided another assistance from the left side of the penalty area to Laotian midfielder Bounpachan Bounkong, who converted it into a score with his right foot.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">In the 33rd minute, midfielder Bounkong scored his second goal and Svay Rieng&rsquo;s third by shooting with his right foot from the edge of the penalty box and placing it in the top right corner of the post. The first half ended with Svay Rieng leading 3-1.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">Halfway through the second half, Svay Rieng&rsquo;s goalkeeper foul played a Shan United player in the penalty area, prompting the referee to give the visiting club a penalty kick. Moussa Bakayoko, the replacement midfielder, took the chance and scored. Svay Rieng&rsquo;s fourth goal came in the 75th minute, scored by attacker Roque. At the end of the contest, Svay Rieng defeated Shan United 4&ndash;2.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">The group stage round for group A was officially completed on Wednesday. Thailand&rsquo;s BG Pathum United finished first in the group, with 11 points. Indonesia&rsquo;s PSM Makassar FC finished second with ten points. Both BG Pathum and PSM advanced to the knockout stage.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">Svay Rieng finished third with seven points, followed by Terengganu FC from Malaysia, with seven points. Vietnam&rsquo;s Đ&ocirc;ng &Aacute; Thanh H&oacute;a FC is placed fifth with six points. Shan United is at the bottom of the group, with no points.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">&ldquo;We intended to conclude the tournament with a win. We are happy with the result, but I believe our players did not give their best yet. The players did not follow our game plan well. I think we did not play at the level that we used to play in the match against Shan United,&rdquo; Pep Munoz, the Head Coach of Svay Rieng said after the match.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">The ASEAN Club Championship is an international football competition organised by the ASEAN Football Federation (AFF) for domestic champion clubs, with FIFA&rsquo;s endorsement</span><br><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">This year&rsquo;s tournament featured 12 top ASEAN football teams divided into two groups.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">The competition follows a single round-robin format in the group stage, where each team plays against all others in their group. The top two teams from each group advance to the knockout stage.</span></p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:39:06', 'uploads/67a6b5baaed81.jpg', 1, 1, NULL, 1),
(64, 'Svay Rieng falls 2-1 to BG Pathum United in ASEAN club championship', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Preah Khan Reach Svay Rieng FC, Cambodia&rsquo;s sole representative in the ASEAN Club was narrowly defeated 2-1 by Thailand&rsquo;s BG Pathum United, in their second group-stage match on Wednesday night at Pathum Thani Stadium, Thailand.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Despite the loss, Svay Rieng FC impressed fans and Cambodian football supporters with their performance, during the match against Thai team, which feature Asian football stars like Teerasil Dangda and Chanathip Songkrasin.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Svay Rieng had more ball possession but struggled to convert their control into goals. BG Pathum United, broke the deadlock in the 31st minute with a strike from Raniel Santana, taking the only goal of the first half.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In the second half, Svay Rieng pushed forward and equalized in the 61st minute with a goal from Brazilian forward Pablo Augusto. However, just two minutes later, BG Pathum United&rsquo;s Teerasil Dangda restored their lead, sealing the 2-1 victory for the home team.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Svay Rieng FC is currently fourth in Group A with three points. Dong A Thanh Hoa FC leads with four points, followed by BG Pathum and PSM Makassar FC in second and third, respectively. Terengganu FC sits in fifth with one point, while Shan United is at the bottom without any points.</p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:40:01', 'uploads/67a6b5f1a5787.jpg', 1, 1, NULL, 1),
(65, 'Newcastle beat Arsenal, return to English League Cup final', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>NEW CASTLE, United Kingdom</strong> &ndash; Newcastle is back in the English League Cup final for another chance to end its 70-year wait for a major domestic trophy.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Saudi-controlled northeast club beat Arsenal 2-0 in the second leg of the semifinals Wednesday to advance 4-0 on aggregate. Jacob Murphy and Anthony Gordon scored the goals at a boisterous St James&rsquo; Park.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Newcastle will play either Tottenham or Liverpool in the March 16 final at Wembley Stadium. Tottenham leads 1-0 after the first leg, with the return match at Anfield on Thursday.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For Newcastle, it marks another opportunity to capture a first piece of silverware since being bought by Saudi Arabia&rsquo;s sovereign wealth fund in 2021. Newcastle&rsquo;s last trophy was the now-defunct Inter-Cities Fairs Cup in 1969 and the most recent domestic title was the FA Cup in 1955.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Newcastle reached the 2023 League Cup final, but lost 2-0 to Manchester United.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Play like that and we can dream big,&rdquo; Newcastle captain Bruno Guimaraes said after the Arsenal match. &ldquo;It would be amazing in my first season as the captain to lift a trophy, it is my dream.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal arrived buoyed by a 5-1 thrashing of Manchester City in the Premier League on Sunday and looking to overturn a 2-0 deficit from the first leg against Newcastle at Emirates Stadium last month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mikel Arteta&rsquo;s team failed to handle the lively atmosphere inside St James&rsquo;, with its usually solid defence looking fragile and almost conceding after just four minutes when Alexander Isak was played through on goal and finished into the top corner. It was disallowed for offside following a video review and the decision was announced to fans inside the stadium by the referee via a wireless microphone &mdash; a practice being trialed in the English League Cup ahead of use in the Premier League.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">After Martin Odegaard hit the post for Arsenal, Newcastle took the lead in the 19th when Isak struck a shot against the post and Murphy converted the rebound.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal&rsquo;s remote chances of a comeback were further hit when Gabriel Martinelli went off with a muscle injury before halftime, and Gordon virtually secured Newcastle&rsquo;s place in the title match by scoring the second after Arsenal midfielder Declan Rice was dispossessed outside his area by a sliding Fabian Schar.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The ball flew straight to Gordon, who swiveled and shot into the bottom corner past stranded goalkeeper David Raya.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal, a two-time League Cup winner, was looking to reach the final for the first time since 2018, when it lost 3-0 to Man City.Newcastle fans taunted Arsenal&rsquo;s manager in the last few minutes, singing: &ldquo;Mikel Arteta, it must be the ball.&rdquo; It was a reference to Arteta saying after the first leg that the ball used in League Cup was &ldquo;different to a Premier League ball.&rdquo;</p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:41:03', 'uploads/67a6b62f5123c.jpg', 1, 1, NULL, 1),
(66, 'Call for contenders to join 3rd National Ju-Jitsu Championship', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Ju-Jitsu Federation of Cambodia (JJFC) is inviting competitors to register for the Third National Ju-Jitsu Championship, which will be held from February 22 to 23 at the Royal University of Phnom Penh (RUPP).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Those who practise and are interested in one of the fastest-growing popular sports, Ju-Jitsu, now have the opportunity to demonstrate their skills at one of the largest Ju-Jitsu events, the National Ju-Jitsu Championship. Interested participants are encouraged to register by or before February 16.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This year&rsquo;s National Ju-Jitsu Championship offers a diverse choice of events for competitors to choose from, depending on the category of their preference.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Female Newaza (GI) division is open to competitors aged 16 and above, with weight classes for -48kg, -57kg, and -63kg. The Female Newaza (No-GI) division includes the -57kg and +57kg weight classes. The Female Fighting division has weight classes for -52kg and -63kg.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Male Newaza (GI) divisions include weight classes -62kg, -69kg, -77kg, and -85kg. The male Newaza (No-GI) is limited to -77kg and +77kg. Male Fighting, on the other hand, is open for -62kg and -77kg weight classes.</p>\r\n<div id=\"khmer-1139222599\" class=\"khmer-content_21\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"khmer-1307761568\" class=\"khmer-content_20\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Third National Ju-Jitsu Championship also includes two kid categories: U16 and U14. The U16 category is open to both boys and girls and has weight limits of -50kg and +50kg, while the U14 division is open to both genders and has weight limits of -38kg and +38kg.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Last year, the Second National Ju-Jitsu Championship included 19 events, with competitors from nine different clubs.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Ministry of Economy and Finance&rsquo;s Ju-Jitsu Association team finished first in the rankings, with eight medals, including five gold, one silver, and two bronze.</p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:42:43', 'uploads/67a6b69334b32.jpg', 1, 1, NULL, 0),
(67, 'Over 400 athletes join Aquathlon School Championships 2025', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Over 400 national and international athletes have participated in the Aquathlon School Championships 2025, marking a 50 percent increase compared to 2024.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngin Sokpanha, Secretary General of the Cambodia Triathlon Federation (CTF), shared this update during the closing ceremony of the tournament at Morodok Techo National Stadium in Phnom Penh on 2nd February.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">He commended the increased number of participants, adding that his federation intends to continue organising such sports events on a large scale in Phnom Penh, as well as in the provinces of Preah Sihanouk and Siem Reap.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The tournament provided a valuable opportunity to promote engagement in sport, allowing athletes to gain experience and strengthen solidarity, he added.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Aquathlon School Championships 2025 was organised into two categories: children&rsquo;s groups (aged from 6 to 8 years, 9 to 11 years, 12 to 14 years, and 15 to 17 years) and adult groups (aged under 39 years and 40 years and above). AKP</p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:43:37', 'uploads/67a6b6c9b8abd.jpg', 1, 1, NULL, 0),
(68, 'Cambodia, Saudi Arabia formalise MoU to boost bilateral trade relations', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Ministry of Commerce of Cambodia and the Minister of Commerce of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia have signed a memorandum of understanding (MoU) aimed at promoting trade relations between the two nations.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The MoU was officially executed on February 6 in Riyadh by Cham Nimul, Minister of Commerce for Cambodia, and Majid bin Abdullah Al-Kassabi, Minister of Commerce and Chairman of the General Authority for Foreign Trade (GAFT) of Saudi Arabia, during Minister Nimul&rsquo;s official visit to Saudi Arabia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">According to the Ministry of Commerce, the primary objective of the MoU is to enhance and diversify trade cooperation, as well as to facilitate and explore new trade opportunities between the two countries.</p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:45:04', 'uploads/67a6b7202c471.jpg', 1, 11, NULL, 1),
(69, 'China pumps $550M into Cambodia’s industrial sector', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Despite ongoing global trade tensions and tariff disputes, China reaffirmed its position as Cambodia&rsquo;s leading Foreign Direct Investment (FDI) by channelling nearly $550 million into the Kingdom&rsquo;s industrial sector in January.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Although the Ministry of Economy and Finance (MEF) has not recorded significant budgets for concession loans and grants since last year, the Council for the Development of Cambodia (CDC) Wednesday confirmed that China&rsquo;s investments continue to surpass any other partner country.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chinese substantial investment accounts for roughly 73.35 percent or an equivalent of $548.65 million compared to Cambodia&rsquo;s overall investment capital of $748 million in the first month of 2025, according to the Cambodian Investment Board (CIB) press release issued on February 5.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">China is among the top investment sources, accounting for 73.35 percent, followed by Vietnam at 5.52 percent, the statement added.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Several experts expressed optimism about the surge in Chinese investment, telling Khmer Times that Cambodia is benefiting from global trade tensions and tariff disputes, which are driving FDI shifts across Southeast Asia.</p>\r\n<div id=\"khmer-1105445371\" class=\"khmer-content_21\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"khmer-1842818519\" class=\"khmer-content_20\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mean Sovannarith, Co-Founder and CEO of DeGrand Realty Co Ltd, noted that the surge in Chinese investment comes as no surprise.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">He highlighted that Cambodia and China have elevated their bilateral relations to an ironclad friendship, underpinned by aligned political and economic strategies.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;In terms of trade, China is the largest import partner, providing affordable products that cater to the needs of the majority of the Cambodian citizens,&rdquo; Sovannarith added.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">He also emphasised the impact of the suspension of the United States Agency for International Development (USAID), which affected over 1,000 workers at the Cambodian Mine Action Centre (CMAC).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;China has stepped in to provide approximately $4.5 million in funding, helping to restore jobs for around 400 mining disposal experts and mitigating the effects of the suspension,&rdquo; the CEO of DeGrand Realty stated.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dr Chey Tech, a socio-economic researcher, pointed out that this marks a substantial increase from previous years with the number of approved projects rising by 300 percent compared to January 2024, mainly in the industrial sector.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;It also shows that China&rsquo;s continued support and investment are playing a crucial role in Cambodia&rsquo;s economic development and growth.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">He went on to add that the strong bilateral relationship commonly known as the &lsquo;Diamond Partnership&rsquo; between Cambodia and China, grounded in mutual trust and respect, has been a key factor in attracting these investments. RCEP and FTA between the two countries have further strengthened trade and investment ties.</p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:45:57', 'uploads/67a6b75582629.jpg', 1, 11, NULL, 1),
(70, 'CMA committed to enhance sustainable microfinance sector', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Cambodian Microfinance Association (CMA) is partnering with the National Bank of Cambodia (NBC) and the United Nations (UN) to protect vulnerable sections and maintain microfinance as a valuable tool for economic empowerment.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Since 2024, NBC and the UN have been engaged in consultations to address key challenges within Cambodia&rsquo;s microfinance sector, including over-indebtedness, land-related financial risks, and consumer protection.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This initiative, now in its active phase, engages over one hundred stakeholders from government bodies, civil society, financial institutions, and development partners to enhance lending practices and ensure the sector&rsquo;s long-term sustainability.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chairwoman of the CMA Dith Nita emphasized the association&rsquo;s commitment to working alongside partners to ensure that microfinance in Cambodia continues to serve those in need.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;We recognize the challenges borrowers face and are actively working to improve lending practices and strengthen consumer protections. Our efforts aim to empower borrowers to make informed decisions while safeguarding their rights,&rdquo; Nita said.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The CMA is also advancing financial literacy programs, particularly targeting women and rural communities through the Safe Community Finance Project, to help borrowers make informed financial decisions and reduce the risk of over-indebtedness.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Together with our partners, we are working to build a financial sector that is inclusive and offers meaningful opportunities for Cambodia&rsquo;s most vulnerable populations. Our goal is to equip borrowers with the tools needed to succeed financially while protecting them from financial risks,&rdquo; she added.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">These efforts align with the United Nations Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs), particularly in the areas of poverty reduction, gender equality, and financial inclusion, ensuring that Cambodia&rsquo;s microfinance sector remains a powerful engine of economic growth and opportunity.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The CMA is focusing on several key areas, including the implementation of enhanced lending standards. In partnership with the NBC and the UN, the CMA is supporting reforms to ensure that loans are granted based on a borrower&rsquo;s ability to repay, rather than relying solely on collateral.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A key measure involves prohibiting the use of Indigenous Communal Land Titles as collateral, thereby protecting vulnerable communities from the risk of land loss.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Additionally, the CMA is supporting the expansion of the Financial Consumer Centre under the Association of Banks in Cambodia, which provides borrowers with access to dispute resolution services and enhanced protections.</p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:46:48', 'uploads/67a6b788bcd64.jpg', 1, 11, NULL, 3),
(71, 'អាជ្ញាធរខេត្តសៀមរាបសង្រ្គោះស្រូវប្រាំងជាង១០០០ហិកតានៅតំបន់ភ្នំក្រោម', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ស្រូវប្រាំងជាង ១០០០ហិកតា នៅសង្កាត់ចុងឃ្នៀស និងសង្កាត់សៀមរាប នៅតំបន់ភ្នំក្រោម ត្រូវបានអាជ្ញាធរជួយសង្គ្រោះ កាលពីដើមសប្ដាហ៍នេះ។</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">នៅថ្ងៃទី៤ ខែកុម្ភៈ ឆ្នាំ២០២៥ ស្រូវប្រាំងរបស់ប្រជាកសិករជាង ១០០០ហិកតា ក្នុងសង្កាត់ចុងឃ្នៀស និងសង្កាត់សៀមរាប ក្រុងសៀមរាប ត្រូវបានអាជ្ញាធរខេត្ដ បានចុះទៅបើកទឹកស្ទឹងសៀមរាប ដើម្បីជួយសង្គ្រោះបន្ទាប់មានការណែនាំពីអភិបាលខេត្ដសៀមរាប។ ការងារនេះ បានជំរុញឱ្យអាជ្ញាធរ​ជំនាញសម្របសម្រួល​ជាមួយក្រុមហ៊ុនស្ថាបនាដងស្ទឹងសៀមរាប បើកទឹកជួយសង្គ្រោះស្រូវប្រាំង​ប្រជាកសិករ។</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">តាមការរាយការណ៍ពីប្រជាកសិករ ស្រូវស្រែប្រាំងរបស់ពួកគេនាឆ្នាំនេះ ប្រឈមនឹងស្វិតស្រពោន ហើយអាចបាត់បង់ទិន្នផលបើសិនជាគ្មានទឹកគ្រប់គ្រាន់។ ពួកគាត់ថា កង្វះទឹកធ្វើស្រែឆ្នាំនេះ ដោយសារស្ថានភាពទឹកទន្លេតិច ហើយទឹកស្ទឹងសៀមរាប ដែលជាប្រភពទឹកហូរធ្លាក់ចូលស្រែ​ជារៀងរាល់ឆ្នាំក៏មានការខ្វះខាត ខណៈដែលស្ទឹងសៀមរាប កំពុងកែលម្អផង។ ប៉ុន្ដែមកដល់ថ្ងៃនេះ អាជ្ញាធរខេត្ដ និងមន្ទីរអង្គភាពពាក់ព័ន្ធ បានបើកទឹកស្ទឹងសៀមរាប បូមដាក់ស្រែទៅតាមតម្រូវការ​ជាបណ្ដើរៗហើយ។ ជាមួយគ្នានេះ ប្រជាកសិករក៏បានថ្លែងអំណរគុណដល់រាជរដ្ឋាភិបាល ជាពិសេសអាជ្ញាធរខេត្ដ និងមន្ទីរអង្គភាពពាក់ព័ន្ធ ដែលផ្ដល់ទឹកជួយសង្គ្រោះស្រូវរបស់គាត់បានចំពេល និងទាន់ពេលវេលា។</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">លោក អ៊ឹង គឹមលាង អភិបាលរងខេត្ត បានណែនាំដល់ប្រជាពលរដ្ឋអំពីការយកចិត្តទុកដាក់​របស់រាជរដ្ឋាភិបាល ក៏ដូចជាអាជ្ញាធរពាក់ព័ន្ធក្នុងការជួយសង្គ្រោះដំណាំស្រូវ​របស់ពលរដ្ឋ​ឱ្យអស់ពីលទ្ធភាព។ តែទោះយ៉ាងនេះក្តី ក្នុងនាមអាជ្ញាធរខេត្ត លោកក៏បានទទូចសុំ​ដល់ពលរដ្ឋកុំធ្វើស្រែប្រាំង​ជាលើកទី២ ព្រោះស្ថានភាពទឹកមិនអំណោយផលនោះទេសម្រាប់ឆ្នាំនេះ៕</p>', 'Sopanha', '2025-02-08 01:53:47', 'uploads/67a6b92bdbf66.jpg', 1, 13, '2025-02-08 02:29:34', 49),
