/a>​<a data-index=\"581\">g</a>​&nbsp;K​<a data-index=\"584\">a</a>​<a data-index=\"585\">tan</a>​<a data-index=\"588\">y</a>​u&nbsp;​<a data-index=\"591\">D</a>​<a data-index=\"592\">ham</a>​s​<a data-index=\"596\">a</a>​<a data-index=\"597\">than</a>​&nbsp;​<a data-index=\"602\">ក្នុង</a>​<a data-index=\"607\">ខេត្ត</a>​<a data-index=\"612\">ចាន់</a>​<a data-index=\"616\">ថា</a>​<a data-index=\"618\">បុរី</a>​&nbsp;​<a data-index=\"623\">បាន</a>​<a data-index=\"626\">ប្រញាប់ប្រញាល់</a>​<a data-index=\"640\">ទៅ</a>​<a data-index=\"642\">ជួយ</a>​<a data-index=\"645\">ពលរដ្ឋ</a>​<a data-index=\"651\">ខ្មែរ</a>​<a data-index=\"656\">ដែល</a>​<a data-index=\"659\">រង</a>​<a data-index=\"661\">របួស</a>​<a data-index=\"665\">នៅកណ្តាល</a>​<a data-index=\"673\">ផ្លូវ</a>​<a data-index=\"678\">។</a>​&nbsp;​<a data-index=\"680\">មនុស្ស</a>​<a data-index=\"686\">៤</a>​<a data-index=\"687\">នាក់</a>​<a data-index=\"691\">ត្រូវ</a>​<a data-index=\"696\">បាន</a>​<a data-index=\"699\">បញ្ជូន</a>​<a data-index=\"705\">ទៅកាន់</a>​<a data-index=\"711\">មន្ទីរពេទ្យ</a>​&nbsp;​<a data-index=\"723\">Ma</a>​k​<a data-index=\"726\">ham</a>​&nbsp;​<a data-index=\"730\">ដើម្បី</a>​<a data-index=\"736\">ព្យាបាល</a>​<a data-index=\"743\">បន្ត</a>​&nbsp;​<a data-index=\"748\">។</a>​</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a data-index=\"750\">បើ</a>​<a data-index=\"752\">តាម</a>​<a data-index=\"755\">ពលករ</a>​<a data-index=\"759\">ខ្មែរ</a>​<a data-index=\"764\">ដែល</a>​<a data-index=\"767\">និយាយ</a>​<a data-index=\"772\">ភាសា</a>​<a data-index=\"776\">ថៃ</a>​<a data-index=\"778\">បានឲ្យ</a>​<a data-index=\"784\">ដឹង</a>​<a data-index=\"787\">ថា</a>​&nbsp;​<a data-index=\"790\">រថយន្ត</a>​<a data-index=\"796\">បាន</a>​<a data-index=\"799\">នឹង</a>​<a data-index=\"802\">កំពុង</a>​<a data-index=\"807\">ដឹក</a>​<a data-index=\"810\">ពលរដ្ឋ</a>​<a data-index=\"816\">ខ្មែរ</a>​<a data-index=\"821\">ត្រឡប់មក</a>​<a data-index=\"829\">ប្រទេស</a>​<a data-index=\"835\">វិញ</a>​&nbsp;​<a data-index=\